{"type":"message","id":"3973cea5","parentId":"eaba86a7","timestamp":"2026-07-07T09:30:44.745Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_28fc98afb13741c9abfdab36","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"var deviceFunctionData = null;\r\nvar functionCacheLoaded = false;\r\n\r\n// v8.40: 定时器状态\r\nvar wbTimerId = null;\r\nvar wbTimerSeconds = 0;\r\nvar focusTimerId = null;\r\nvar focusTimerSeconds = 0;\r\n\r\n// v6.20 + v7.0: 禁用所有控制区域(PTZ + 媒体 + 跟踪 + 画面)\r\nfunction disableImageControls(reason) {\r\n    // v7.30: 模块级别禁用灰色样式\r\n    var sections = ['ptzControlSection', 'trackControlSection', 'mediaControlSection', 'imageControlSection', 'logControlSection'];\r\n    sections.forEach(function(sectionId) {\r\n        var section = document.getElementById(sectionId);\r\n        if (section) {\r\n            section.classList.add('section-disabled');\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n\r\n\n[1461 more lines in file. Use offset=615 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783416644745}}
{"type":"message","id":"bff9192c","parentId":"3973cea5","timestamp":"2026-07-07T09:30:44.746Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_afa6a5d9a0cd4dd48b40fe2c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    // v7.54: 支持多种曝光模式\r\n    var mode = exposureMode.value;\r\n    var shutterEnabled = (mode === 'manual' || mode === 'ShutterFirst');\r\n    var irisEnabled = (mode === 'manual' || mode === 'IrisFirst');\r\n    var gainEnabled = (mode === 'manual' || mode === 'ShutterFirst' || mode === 'IrisFirst');\r\n    shutterSelect.disabled = !shutterEnabled;\r\n    irisSelect.disabled = !irisEnabled;\r\n    if (gainSlider) gainSlider.disabled = !gainEnabled;\r\n\r\n    // v8.40: 自动模式时隐藏快门/光圈/增益\r\n    var shutterRow = shutterSelect.parentElement.parentElement;\r\n    var gainRow = gainSlider ? gainSlider.parentElement : null;\r\n    if (mode === 'auto') {\r\n        shutterRow.style.display = 'none';\r\n        if (gainRow) gainRow.style.display = 'none';\r\n    } else {\r\n        shutterRow.style.display = '';\r\n        if (gainRow) gainRow.style.display = '';\r\n        shutterSelect.style.opacity = shutterEnabled ? '1' : '0.5';\r\n        irisSelect.style.opacity = irisEnabled ? '1' : '0.5';\r\n        if (gainSlider) gainSlider.style.opacity = gainEnabled ? '1' : '0.5';\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 设置快门\r\nfunction setShutterSpeed(value) {\r\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\r\n    if (!dev) return;\r\n    apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/shutter', { level: value })\r\n        .then(function(r) {\r\n\n[256 more lines in file. Use offset=1820 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783416644745}}
{"type":"message","id":"d5ba14a9","parentId":"bff9192c","timestamp":"2026-07-07T09:31:30.667Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我整理一下发现问题：\n\n## 问题1：初始值逻辑缺失\n\n需求：\n- 如果之前的模式是自动，那就 R/B=50/50 起步\n- 如果之前是手动或者局部，就从当前值开始\n\n现状：\n- `WhiteBalanceSearcher.__init__()` 接受 `current_red` 和 `current_blue` 参数\n- `router.py` 的 `whitebalance_search` 端点没有读取当前模式\n- 无法判断之前是 自动/手动/局部，无从判断默认值应该是 50/50 还是当前值\n\n需要修改：\n1. **router.py** `/vision/whitebalance-search` 端点：调用 `/ptz/{device_id}/image/whitebalance` 获取当前模式和增益值\n2. 判断：\n   - 如果 `mode == 'auto'` → `current_red = 100, current_blue = 100`（不是50/50，设备默认值）\n   - 如果 `mode == 'manual' || 'local'` → 使用读取到的 `red_gain, blue_gain`\n3. 传递给 `WhiteBalanceSearcher`\n\n## 问题2：三级步进策略已存在\n\n现状：\n- `IterativeWB` 类已经实现了三级步进策略：\n  - `_stage_steps = [5, 2, 1]` 粗调(>500) / 中调(>=50) / 精调(<50)\n  - `_stage_min = [6, 3, 0]` 阶段升级条件\n\n代码分析显示，步进策略直接硬编码在代码中，不依赖 `red_gain`。但需求明确要求根据增益值动态调整步进：\n- red_gain >= 500 → 粗调 ±5\n- red_gain >= 50 → 中调 ±2\n- red_gain < 50 → 精调 ±1\n\n这需要修改算法判断逻辑，根据增益值动态调整搜索阶段和步进大小。\n\n## 问题3：下拉菜单bug\n\n拷贝问题指用户操作后下拉菜单未能正确切换。\n\n`onWbModeChange` 函数存在逻辑缺陷，切换到\"自动\"和\"局部\"模式时会直接触发 `setWhiteBalanceMode('auto')`，导致显示异常。需要重新审视模式切换和UI渲染机制。\n\n，看不到 `_wb_searcher._best_red/_best_blue`，无法停止搜索。\n\n问题根源可能是搜索未发起或中断标志未生效。\n\n我仔细检查代码：`stopAutoWhiteBalance` 调用了 `_wb_searcher._interrupt()` 方法，理论上应该能中断搜索。但当前控制台没有发送搜索命令，所以 `_wb_searcher` 仍然是 `None`。这意味着搜索根本没有启动。\n\n可能是定时器配置失误（如设置为0或未正确启动），导致搜索未实际执行。\n\n需要检查 `toggleWbTimer` 函数的具体实现和定时器触发机制。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_bbdaaf7e5de1475a84dc740f","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":280,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":40154,"output":657,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40811,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783416644746,"responseId":"cht000d721e@dx19f3bea9d9b29c2503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5567807a","parentId":"d5ba14a9","timestamp":"2026-07-07T09:31:30.673Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_bbdaaf7e5de1475a84dc740f","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                                            <button id=\"btnWbRegionSelect\" class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onclick=\"toggleRegionMode('whitebalance')\" style=\"flex-shrink:0;padding:4px 8px\">框选</button>\r\n                                            <input type=\"text\" id=\"wbTimerInput\" value=\"\" placeholder=\"定时\" style=\"flex:1;min-width:0;padding:4px 6px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:6px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:10px\" oninput=\"updateWbTimerInput(this)\">\r\n                                            <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:10px;white-space:nowrap\">min</span>\r\n                                            <label class=\"switch\" style=\"flex-shrink:0\" title=\"打开应用定时\">\r\n                                                <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"wbTimerToggle\" onchange=\"toggleWbTimer()\">\r\n                                                <span class=\"slider\"></span>\r\n                                            </label>\r\n                                            <button id=\"btnWbLocalStop\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-sm\" onclick=\"stopAutoWhiteBalance()\" disabled style=\"opacity:0.5;flex-shrink:0;padding:4px 8px\">停止</button>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div id=\"wbTimerDisplay\" style=\"color:#f85149;font-size:11px;text-align:center;margin-top:2px\"></div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 对焦 -->\r\n                                    <div class=\"form-group\" style=\"margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">对焦</label>\r\n                                        <select id=\"focusMode\" style=\"width:100%;padding:4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:12px\" onchange=\"onFocusModeChange(this.value)\">\r\n                                            <option value=\"auto\">自动</option>\r\n                                            <option value=\"manual\">手动</option>\r\n                                            <option value=\"local\">局部</option>\r\n                                        </select>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 焦点移动按钮(仅手动模式显示) -->\r\n                                    <div id=\"focusMoveControls\" style=\"display:none;margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap\">\r\n                                            <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">焦点:</span>\r\n                                            <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzFocus('far')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" ontouchstart=\"ptzFocus('far')\" ontouchend=\"ptzStop()\">远</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzFocus('near')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" ontouchstart=\"ptzFocus('near')\" ontouchend=\"ptzStop()\">近</button>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 局部对焦控制(仅局部模式显示) -->\r\n                                    <div id=\"focusLocalControls\" style=\"display:none;margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;width:100%\">\r\n                                            <button id=\"btnFocusRegionSelect\" class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onclick=\"toggleRegionMode('focus')\" style=\"flex-shrink:0;padding:4px 8px\">框选</button>\r\n                                            <input type=\"text\" id=\"focusTimerInput\" value=\"\" placeholder=\"定时\" style=\"flex:1;min-width:0;padding:4px 6px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:6px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:10px\" oninput=\"updateFocusTimerInput(this)\">\r\n                                            <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:10px;white-space:nowrap\">min</span>\r\n                                            <label class=\"switch\" style=\"flex-shrink:0\" title=\"打开应用定时\">\r\n                                                <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"focusTimerToggle\" onchange=\"toggleFocusTimer()\">\r\n                                                <span class=\"slider\"></span>\r\n                                            </label>\r\n                                            <button id=\"btnFocusLocalStop\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-sm\" onclick=\"stopAutoFocus()\" disabled style=\"opacity:0.5;flex-shrink:0;padding:4px 8px\">停止</button>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div id=\"focusTimerDisplay\" style=\"color:#f85149;font-size:11px;text-align:center;margin-top:2px\"></div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 曝光模式 + 快门/光圈 (v5.47: 整合到一行) -->\r\n                                    <div class=\"form-group\" style=\"margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">曝光模式</label>\r\n                                        <select id=\"exposureMode\" style=\"width:100%;padding:4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:12px\" onchange=\"setExposureMode(this.value);updateShutterIrisState()\">\r\n                                            <!-- v7.35: 从 function.json 动态加载 -->\r\n                                        </select>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 快门/光圈整合一行 -->\r\n\n[1746 more lines in fi