{"type":"message","id":"57324194","parentId":"ea10c5e6","timestamp":"2026-07-07T12:14:05.678Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"后端语法检查通过了。现在检查前端 console.html 的语法。前端应该用浏览器检查，但我可以用 Node 检查基本的语法或至少检查引号是否闭合。\n\n让我再仔细检查一下 whitebalance.py 中的修改：\n1. _read_wb_status() 定义是否正确\n2. run() 中的逻辑是否正确\n3. 中断处理是否正确\n\n让我看看完整的 run() 函数开头部分。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_057353864e7648dbaf12fd27","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":208,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\controlpanel\\whitebalance.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":61230,"output":137,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61367,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783426419159,"responseId":"cht000df239@dx19f3c7fbb722872503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"71a5c636","parentId":"57324194","timestamp":"2026-07-07T12:14:05.685Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_057353864e7648dbaf12fd27","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<WhiteBalance version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\n<WhiteBalanceStyle>manual</WhiteBalanceStyle>\n<WhiteBalanceRed>{red}</WhiteBalanceRed>\n<WhiteBalanceBlue>{blue}</WhiteBalanceBlue>\n</WhiteBalance>'''\n        resp = self.client.put(\"/Image/channels/1/whiteBalance\", xml)\n        return resp.status_code == 200\n    \n    def _read_wb_status(self):\n        \"\"\"读取当前白平衡状态（模式+增益）- v8.62\"\"\"\n        try:\n            resp = self.client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/whiteBalance\")\n            if resp.status_code == 200:\n                import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n                root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\n                mode = \"auto\"\n                red, blue = 100, 100\n                for elem in root.iter():\n                    tag = elem.tag.split('}')[-1] if '}' in elem.tag else elem.tag\n                    if tag in (\"WhiteBalanceStyle\", \"whiteBalanceStyle\"):\n                        mode = (elem.text or \"auto\").lower()\n                    elif tag in (\"WhiteBalanceRed\", \"whiteBalanceRed\"):\n                        red = int(elem.text)\n                    elif tag in (\"WhiteBalanceBlue\", \"whiteBalanceBlue\"):\n                        blue = int(elem.text)\n                return mode, red, blue\n        except:\n            pass\n        return \"auto\", 100, 100\n    \n    def _capture(self):\n        \"\"\"截取框选区域\"\"\"\n        bgr, crop_path, info = self._capture_func(\n            self.client, self.mgr, self.device_ip, \"WB\",\n            self.x, self.y, self.w, self.h\n        )\n        return bgr, info\n    \n    def _interrupt(self):\n        \"\"\"v8.41: 中断白平衡搜索\"\"\"\n        self._interrupted = True\n    \n    async def run(self):\n        \"\"\"运行白平衡搜索，产生SSE事件\"\"\"\n        \n        # 1. 读取当前模式+增益（v8.62）\n        current_mode, current_red, current_blue = await asyncio.to_thread(self._read_wb_status)\n        \n        # 2. 切换手动白平衡模式\n        ok = await asyncio.to_thread(self._set_wb_mode, \"manual\")\n\n[102 more lines in file. Use offset=258 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783426445685}}
{"type":"message","id":"c9eab9d8","parentId":"71a5c636","timestamp":"2026-07-07T12:16:05.015Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"后端白平衡修正检查清单：\n- 是否新增了 _read_wb_status（mode + red_salt + blue_salt）✅\n- 是否在 run() 开头调用了 _read_wb_status（当前模式 + R/B 初始值）✅\n- if current_mode == \"auto\"：50/50 初始值、写入设备 ✅\n- else locked/manual：使用读取到的 R/B 作为初始值 ✅\n- 中断处理的 best_red/best_blue bug：从 wb._best_red/best_blue 获取 ✅\n\n前端 console.html 检查清单：\n- loadWhiteBalance locked → local 映射 ✅\n- onWbModeChange auto stopWbTimer + 重置钩子 ✅\n- stopWbTimer：准备在 stopFocusTimer 之前定义 ✅\n\n下一步：完成后端语法验证，转前端检查与测试准备汇报。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"后端修改完成且语法检查通过。console.html 需浏览器端验证。\n\n## 修改汇总（v8.62）\n\n### 后端 `whitebalance.py`\n\n1. `_read_wb_status()` - 新增：返回 (mode, red, blue)\n2. `run()` - 改进步骤：\n   - 先读取当前模式+增益\n   - auto → 初始 50/50，写入设备\n   - locked/manual → 使用当前值\n3. 中断处理 - 修复：从 wb._best_red/best_blue 读取\n\n### 前端 `console.html`\n\n1. `loadWhiteBalance()` - 增加 locked → local 映射\n2. `onWbModeChange()` - auto 时调用 stopWbTimer() + 重置钩子\n3. `stopWbTimer()` - 补充函数定义（待执行）\n\n修复准备完毕。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":61864,"output":382,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62246,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783426445686,"responseId":"cht000d0caa@dx19f3c8158e22872503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"9d785024","parentId":"c9eab9d8","timestamp":"2026-07-07T12:23:05.597Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"47918\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-07-07 20:23 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n现在检查\n1. 自动对焦的定时启动、停止，下拉菜单选其他模式之后，是怎么样的？有没有实现用户点击开关启动，启动状态下切换别的模式就停止计数、定时功能。同时再检查局部白平衡是否也实现了\n2. 白平衡5、2、1的步进是怎么样的逻辑？"}],"timestamp":1783426985594}}
{"type":"message","id":"56af7de6","parentId":"9d785024","timestamp":"2026-07-07T12:23:21.680Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板要我检查两个问题：\n\n1. 定时启动/停止机制：\n   - 自动对焦的定时\n   - 自动白平衡的定时\n   - 切换模式后是否会停止计数/定时\n   - 局部白平衡是否也实现了定时功能\n   - 需要检查前端实现逻辑\n\n2. 白平衡5、2、1步进逻辑：\n   - 需要检查 IterativeWB 的步进策略\n   - 是如何根据增益值决定步进大小\n\n让我先检查前端的定时器实现。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"老板要我检查两个问题，我先读取两个定时器相关的代码。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c2a73e65745c48bea2cd9809","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":80,"offset":1251,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":62467,"output":179,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62646,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783426985598,"responseId":"cht000df966@dx19f3c8832592871503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"db0fd082","parentId":"56af7de6","timestamp":"2026-07-07T12:23:21.691Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c2a73e65745c48bea2cd9809","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// 设置白平衡模式\r\n// 白平衡模式切换:显示/隐藏对应控件\r\nfunction onWbModeChange(mode) {\r\n    var manualControls = document.getElementById('wbManualControls');\r\n    var localControls = document.getElementById('wbLocalControls');\r\n    var wbRed = document.getElementById('wbRed');\r\n    var wbBlue = document.getElementById('wbBlue');\r\n\r\n    if (mode === 'manual') {\r\n        if (manualControls) manualControls.style.display = 'flex';\r\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        if (wbRed) wbRed.disabled = false;\r\n        if (wbBlue) wbBlue.disabled = false;\r\n        setWhiteBalanceMode('manual');\r\n    } else if (mode === 'local') {\r\n        if (manualControls) manualControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'block';\r\n        if (wbRed) wbRed.disabled = true;\r\n        if (wbBlue) wbBlue.disabled = true;\r\n        // v8.39: 局部模式自动切换到手动模式\r\n        setWhiteBalanceMode('manual');\r\n    } else {\r\n        // 自动\r\n        if (manualControls) manualControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        if (wbRed) wbRed.disabled = true;\r\n        if (wbBlue) wbBlue.disabled = true;\r\n        setWhiteBalanceMode('auto');\r\n        // v8.60: 切自动时关闭定时器\r\n        stopWbTimer();\r\n        var toggle = document.getElementById('wbTimerToggle');\r\n        if (toggle) toggle.checked = false;\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 停止自动白平衡\r\nfunction stopAutoWhiteBalance() {\r\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\r\n    if (!dev) return;\r\n    if (typeof operationLog === 'function') operationLog('用户停止', 'warning');\r\n    apiPost('/api/v1/vision/whitebalance-stop', {}).then(function(r) {\r\n        if (r && r.success) {\r\n            showToast('success', '已停止白平衡搜索');\r\n        }\r\n    }).catch(function(e) {\r\n        showToast('error', '停止失败');\r\n    });\r\n    // 恢复按钮状态\r\n    var stopBtn = document.getElementById('btnWbLocalStop');\r\n    var confirmBtn = document.getElementById('btnWbTimerConfirm');\r\n    var selectBtn = document.getElementById('btnWbRegionSelect');\r\n    if (stopBtn) stopBtn.disabled = true;\r\n    if (confirmBtn) { confirmBtn.disabled = true; confirmBtn.style.opacity = '0.5'; }\r\n    if (selectBtn) { selectBtn.style.opacity = '1'; }\r\n    selectBtn.style.opacity = '1';\r\n    stopWbTimer();\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 对焦模式切换:显示/隐藏对应控件\r\nfunction onFocusModeChange(mode) {\r\n    var moveControls = document.getElementById('focusMoveControls');\r\n    var localControls = document.getElementById('focusLocalControls');\r\n\r\n    if (mode === 'manual') {\r\n        if (moveControls) moveControls.style.display = 'block';\r\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        setFocusMode('manual');\r\n    } else if (mode === 'local') {\r\n        if (moveControls) moveControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'block';\r\n    } else {\r\n        // 自动\r\n        if (moveControls) moveControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        setFocusMode('auto');\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 停止自动对焦\r\nfunction stopAutoFocus() {\r\n\n[758 more lines in file. Use offset=1331 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783427001691}}
