{"type":"message","id":"2fbe2304","parentId":"09072628","timestamp":"2026-07-07T12:28:24.738Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在让我检查 IterativeWB 的步进逻辑："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_705eee0785484c09baee0e90","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"offset":1,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\controlpanel\\whitebalance.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":67287,"output":59,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67346,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783427296144,"responseId":"cht000d5acd@dx19f3c8cf5c329c2503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"521db1af","parentId":"2fbe2304","timestamp":"2026-07-07T12:28:24.746Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_705eee0785484c09baee0e90","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"AstroHub v8.37 - 白平衡模块\n\n包含：\n- IterativeWB: 纯算法迭代搜索\n- WhiteBalanceSearcher: 执行层（截图、设置增益、验证、SSE事件）\n\"\"\"\n\nimport json\nimport asyncio\nfrom .region_base import _rgb_stats, calc_stable_delay\n\n\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────\n# 纯算法层：迭代搜索\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────\n\nclass IterativeWB:\n    \"\"\"白平衡迭代搜索器 - R/B 独立调整\n    \n    状态：粗调(±5) → 中调(±2) → 精调(±1)\n    每步评估 [双通道, 仅R, 仅B] 三个候选，选 delta 最小。\n    全程追踪 best_gains + best_delta，结束时回滚到最佳。\n    \n    输入：BGR图像\n    输出：dict（action, red_gain, blue_gain, delta, message等）\n    \n    不涉及任何设备操作，纯粹数学逻辑。\n    \"\"\"\n\n    def __init__(self, current_red=100, current_blue=100):\n        self._stage = 0\n        self._stage_steps = [5, 2, 1]\n        self._stage_min = [6, 3, 0]\n        self._tolerances = [0.70, 0.80, 0.95]\n        self._current_red = current_red\n        self._current_blue = current_blue\n        self._no_improve = 0\n        self._stage_step_count = 0\n        self._fine_steps = 0\n        self._best_red = current_red\n        self._best_blue = current_blue\n        self._best_delta = 999.0\n        self._best_step = 0\n        self._step_count = 0\n\n    def _eval(self, r_sum, g_sum, b_sum, red, blue) -> float:\n        \"\"\"评估RGB平衡程度\"\"\"\n        if g_sum < 1: g_sum = 1\n        ar = max(1, r_sum) * red / max(1, self._current_red)\n        ab = max(1, b_sum) * blue / max(1, self._current_blue)\n        return abs(ar / g_sum - 1.0) + abs(ab / g_sum - 1.0)\n\n    def step(self, bgr) -> dict:\n        \"\"\"输入BGR图像，返回下一步动作\"\"\"\n        stats = _rgb_stats(bgr)\n        n = stats[\"n\"]\n        r_sum, g_sum, b_sum = stats[\"r_sum\"], stats[\"g_sum\"], stats[\"b_sum\"]\n\n        self._step_count += 1\n        self._stage_step_count += 1\n        step = self._stage_steps[self._stage]\n\n        # 计算候选增益\n        cr = self._current_red + max(-step, min(step, int(g_sum / max(1, r_sum) * self._current_red) - self._current_red))\n        cb = self._current_blue + max(-step, min(step, int(g_sum / max(1, b_sum) * self._current_blue) - self._current_blue))\n        cr = max(1, min(255, cr))\n        cb = max(1, min(255, cb))\n\n        # 候选列表 (- stage 2: R/B独立调整)\n        if self._stage == 2:\n            # 精调阶段：全部R/B独立，无\"both\"候选\n            candidates = [(cr, self._current_blue, \"red\"), (self._current_red, cb, \"blue\")]\n        else:\n            candidates = [(cr, cb, \"both\"), (cr, self._current_blue, \"red\"), (self._current_red, cb, \"blue\")]\n\n        # 选最优候选\n        best_cand = None\n        best_d = 999.0\n        for r, b, label in candidates:\n            d = self._eval(r_sum, g_sum, b_sum, r, b)\n            if d < best_d:\n                best_d = d\n                best_cand = (r, b, label)\n\n        new_red, new_blue, direction = best_cand\n        new_red = int(new_red)\n        new_blue = int(new_blue)\n\n        # 计算当前delta\n        actual = abs(r_sum / max(1, g_sum) - 1.0) + abs(b_sum / max(1, g_sum) - 1.0)\n\n        # 更新best\n        prev_best = self._best_delta\n        if actual < self._best_delta:\n            self._best_delta = actual\n            self._best_red = self._current_red\n            self._best_blue = self._current_blue\n            self._best_step = self._step_count\n\n        # 无改善计数\n\n[259 more lines in file. Use offset=101 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783427304746}}
{"type":"message","id":"9641f783","parentId":"521db1af","timestamp":"2026-07-07T12:28:36.488Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_537694d611e541799521e959","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":60,"offset":101,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\controlpanel\\whitebalance.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":68411,"output":48,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68459,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783427304748,"responseId":"cht000d4d54@dx19f3c8d2cc82871503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"bea15f9c","parentId":"9641f783","timestamp":"2026-07-07T12:28:36.493Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_537694d611e541799521e959","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        tolerance = self._tolerances[self._stage]\n        if actual >= prev_best * tolerance:\n            self._no_improve += 1\n        else:\n            self._no_improve = 0\n\n        stage_name = [\"coarse\", \"medium\", \"fine\"][self._stage]\n        min_steps = self._stage_min[self._stage]\n\n        # 阶段升级\n        if self._stage < 2 and self._stage_step_count >= min_steps and self._no_improve >= 2:\n            self._stage += 1\n            self._stage_step_count = 0\n            self._no_improve = 0\n            # 进入精调时重置best追踪，避免粗调阶段的best覆盖精调结果\n            if self._stage == 2:\n                self._best_delta = 999.0\n                self._best_red = self._current_red\n                self._best_blue = self._current_blue\n                self._best_step = self._step_count\n            new_stage = [\"medium\", \"fine\"][self._stage - 1]\n            return {\n                \"action\": \"continue\",\n                \"stage\": new_stage,\n                \"step_size\": self._stage_steps[self._stage],\n                \"red_gain\": self._current_red, \"blue_gain\": self._current_blue,\n                \"r_avg\": round(stats[\"r_avg\"], 1), \"g_avg\": round(stats[\"g_avg\"], 1), \"b_avg\": round(stats[\"b_avg\"], 1),\n                \"delta\": round(actual, 4), \"best_delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"pixels\": n,\n                \"message\": f\"进入{'中等' if self._stage == 1 else '精细'}调校 (step=±{self._stage_steps[self._stage]})\"\n            }\n\n        # 精调阶段处理\n        if self._stage == 2:\n            self._fine_steps += 1\n            if self._no_improve >= 3 or self._fine_steps >= 10:\n                rollback = (self._best_red != self._current_red or self._best_blue != self._current_blue)\n                self._current_red = self._best_red\n                self._current_blue = self._best_blue\n                return {\n                    \"action\": \"stop\",\n                    \"stage\": \"done\",\n                    \"step_size\": 0,\n                    \"red_gain\": self._best_red, \"blue_gain\": self._best_blue,\n                    \"r_avg\": round(stats[\"r_avg\"], 1), \"g_avg\": round(stats[\"g_avg\"], 1), \"b_avg\": round(stats[\"b_avg\"], 1),\n                    \"delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"best_delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"pixels\": n,\n                    \"message\": f\"白平衡完成 {'(回滚至最佳)' if rollback else '(已达最佳)'} 第{self._best_step}步\"\n                }\n\n        # 应用新增益\n        self._current_red = new_red\n        self._current_blue = new_blue\n        return {\n            \"action\": \"continue\",\n            \"stage\": stage_name,\n            \"step_size\": step,\n            \"red_gain\": new_red, \"blue_gain\": new_blue,\n            \"r_avg\": round(stats[\"r_avg\"], 1), \"g_avg\": round(stats[\"g_avg\"], 1), \"b_avg\": round(stats[\"b_avg\"], 1),\n            \"delta\": round(actual, 4), \"best_delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"pixels\": n,\n            \"message\": f\"{'粗' if self._stage == 0 else '中' if self._stage == 1 else '精'}调 {direction} (±{step})\"\n        }\n\n[199 more lines in file. Use offset=161 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783427316493}}
{"type":"message","id":"d412d260","parentId":"bea15f9c","timestamp":"2026-07-07T12:29:24.087Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的，现在我已经看到了完整的代码。让我整理分析结果。\n\n## 检查结果\n\n### 问题1：定时器启停机制\n\n#### 白平衡定时器\n\n| 场景 | 现状 | 是否正确 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| 用户打开开关 | `toggleWbTimer()` → 启动 `setInterval` | ✅ |\n| 用户关闭开关 | `toggleWbTimer()` → `stopWbTimer()` | ✅ |\n| 定时到达 → 执行搜索 | `executeScheduledSearch('whitebalance')` | ✅ |\n| 搜索完成 → 重启定时 | `wbTimerId === null` → 重新倒计时 | ✅ |\n| 切\"自动\"模式 → 停止定时 | `onWbModeChange('auto')` → `stopWbTimer()` + checkbox | ✅ v8.62已修 |\n| 切\"手动\"模式 → 停止定时 | **未调用 `stopWbTimer()`** | ❌ 缺失 |\n| 切\"局部\"模式 → 停止定时 | **未调用 `stopWbTimer()`** | ❌ 缺失 |\n| 点击\"停止\"按钮 | `stopAutoWhiteBalance()` → `stopWbTimer()` | ✅ |\n\n#### 对焦定时器\n\n| 场景 | 现状 | 是否正确 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| 用户打开开关 | `toggleFocusTimer()` → 启动 `setInterval` | ✅ |\n| 用户关闭开关 | `toggleFocusTimer()` → `stopFocusTimer()` | ✅ |\n| 定时到达 → 执行搜索 | `executeScheduledSearch('focus')` | ✅ |\n| 搜索完成 → 重启定时 | `focusTimerId === null` → 重新倒计时 | ✅ |\n| 切\"自动\"模式 → 停止定时 | **未调用 `stopFocusTimer()`** | ❌ 缺失 |\n| 切\"手动\"模式 → 停止定时 | **未调用 `stopFocusTimer()`** | ❌ 缺失 |\n| 切\"局部\"模式 → 停止定时 | **未调用 `stopFocusTimer()`** | ❌ 缺失 |\n| 点击\"停止\"按钮 | `stopAutoFocus()` → `stopFocusTimer()` | ✅ |\n\n**核心问题**：`onWbModeChange` 和 `onFocusModeChange` 在切换到任何模式时，都应先停止对应定时器。当前只有白平衡切\"自动\"时停止（v8.62刚加的），其余5个分支都缺失。\n\n---\n\n### 问题2：白平衡 5/2/1 步进逻辑\n\n`IterativeWB` 类的步进策略：\n\n```\n_stage_steps = [5, 2, 1]     # 步进大小\n_stage_min = [6, 3, 0]       # 最小步数（升级前必须执行）\n_tolerances = [0.70, 0.80, 0.95]  # 改善容忍度\n```\n\n**阶段升级逻辑**（非基于增益值，基于改善率）：\n1. **粗调 (stage=0)**: 步进 ±5，至少执行6步，连续2步无改善 → 升级到中调\n2. **中调 (stage=1)**: 步进 ±2，至少执行3步，连续2步无改善 → 升级到精调\n3. **精调 (stage=2)**: 步进 ±1，连续3步无改善 或 最多10步 → 完成\n\n**与老板需求对比**：\n- 老板说的 `>=500 粗调±5, >=50 中调±2, <50 精调±1` — 这是按 **增益值** 决定阶段\n- 实际代码是按 **改善率** 决定阶段升级，不是按增益值\n- 代码的步进大小 [5, 2, 1] 与老板需求一致，但 **升级条件不同**\n\n---\n\n### 修复计划\n\n#### 修改1：`onWbModeChange` — 所有分支停止定时器\n\n**文件**: `console.html`\n**修改**: 在函数开头统一调用 `stopWbTimer()` + 重置 checkbox\n\n#### 修改2：`onFocusModeChange` — 所有分支停止定时器\n\n**文件**: `console.html`  \n**修改**: 在函数开头统一调用 `stopFocusTimer()` + 重置 checkbox\n\n#### 关于步进逻辑\n\n老板说\"算法层面、停止等待等逻辑完全不变\"。当前步进 [5, 2, 1] 和升级条件（改善率驱动）是已有逻辑。如果老板认为升级条件需要改为按增益值判断，这是算法层修改，需要老板确认。\n\n是否继续修复定时器问题？步进逻辑是否需要改？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":69276,"output":1057,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70333,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783427316495,"responseId":"cht000dd982@dx19f3c8daeee2872503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a93488bc","parentId":"d412d260","timestamp":"2026-07-07T12:33:20.183Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"47930\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-07-07 20:33 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n1. 切\"局部\"模式 → 停止定时，这个是不需要的，因为目前已经在局部模式，才有计时功能，再点击局部，不应该停止。白平衡和对焦都是一样\n2. 白平衡逻辑调整：\n粗调 (stage=0): 步进 ±5，无数步，直到满足阈值<=100。中调 (stage=1): 步进 ±2，无数步，直到满足阈值，直到<10。精调 (stage=2): 步进 ±1，上限20步，或者直到获得0.1以内的delta\n备份后修改，迭代版本号，精确修复，禁止过度开发，引入新脚本"}],"timestamp":1783427600177}}
