{"type":"message","id":"3c217d4a","parentId":"b5b615f7","timestamp":"2026-07-07T12:38:19.942Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good! I updated the `onWbModeChange` function. Now I need to do the same for `onFocusModeChange`.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"### 修改2：前 console.html - 对焦定时器停止逻辑"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_912ee8c77fe744aaab43f3ff","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"// 对焦模式切换:显示/隐藏对应控件\nfunction onFocusModeChange(mode) {\n    var moveControls = document.getElementById('focusMoveControls');\n    var localControls = document.getElementById('focusLocalControls');\n\n    if (mode === 'manual') {\n        if (moveControls) moveControls.style.display = 'block';\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'none';\n        setFocusMode('manual');\n        // v8.63: 切手动时停止定时器\n        stopFocusTimer();\n        var toggle = document.getElementById('focusTimerToggle');\n        if (toggle) toggle.checked = false;\n    } else if (mode === 'local') {\n        if (moveControls) moveControls.style.display = 'none';\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'block';\n        // v8.63: 局部模式下不需要停止定时器\n    } else {\n        // 自动\n        if (moveControls) moveControls.style.display = 'none';\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'none';\n        setFocusMode('auto');\n        // v8.63: 切自动时停止定时器\n        stopFocusTimer();\n        var toggle = document.getElementById('focusTimerToggle');\n        if (toggle) toggle.checked = false;\n    }\n}","oldText":"// 对焦模式切换:显示/隐藏对应控件\nfunction onFocusModeChange(mode) {\n    var moveControls = document.getElementById('focusMoveControls');\n    var localControls = document.getElementById('focusLocalControls');\n\n    if (mode === 'manual') {\n        if (moveControls) moveControls.style.display = 'block';\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'none';\n        setFocusMode('manual');\n    } els