{"type":"message","id":"83fb817b","parentId":"98055757","timestamp":"2026-07-07T12:41:08.498Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_18facd855b3e475ca0c1220e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            if self._fine_steps >= 20 or actual < 0.1:\n                rollback = (self._best_red != self._current_red or self._best_blue != self._current_blue)\n                self._current_red = self._best_red\n                self._current_blue = self._best_blue\n                return {\n                    \"action\": \"stop\",\n                    \"stage\": \"done\",\n                    \"step_size\": 0,\n                    \"red_gain\": self._best_red, \"blue_gain\": self._best_blue,\n                    \"r_avg\": round(stats[\"r_avg\"], 1), \"g_avg\": round(stats[\"g_avg\"], 1), \"b_avg\": round(stats[\"b_avg\"], 1),\n                    \"delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"best_delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"pixels\": n,\n                    \"message\": f\"白平衡完成 {'(回滚至最佳)' if rollback else '(已达最佳)'} 第{self._best_step}步\"\n                }\n\n        # 应用新增益\n        self._current_red = new_red\n        self._current_blue = new_blue\n        return {\n            \"action\": \"continue\",\n            \"stage\": stage_name,\n            \"step_size\": step,\n            \"red_gain\": new_red, \"blue_gain\": new_blue,\n            \"r_avg\": round(stats[\"r_avg\"], 1), \"g_avg\": round(stats[\"g_avg\"], 1), \"b_avg\": round(stats[\"b_avg\"], 1),\n            \"delta\": round(actual, 4), \"best_delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"pixels\": n,\n            \"message\": f\"{'粗' if self._stage == 0 else '中' if self._stage == 1 else '精'}调 {direction} (±{step})\"\n        }\n\n\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────\n# 执行层：协调设备操作\n\n[195 more lines in file. Use offset=165 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783428068498}}
{"type":"message","id":"0e354247","parentId":"83fb817b","timestamp":"2026-07-07T12:42:05.375Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good! The code looks correct. Let me verify the changes are complete:\n\n1. ✅ Backend: `iteration.py` - Modified `IterativeWB` class:\n   - Removed `_stage_min` and `_tolerances`\n   - Added `_stage_thresholds = [100, 10, 0.1]`\n   - Modified stage upgrade logic from `stage_step_count >= min_steps and no_improve >= 2` to `actual <= _stage_thresholds[stage]`\n   - Modified fine stage logic from `no_improve >= 3 or fine_steps >= 10` to `fine_steps >= 20 or actual < 0.1`\n\n2. ✅ Frontend: `console.html` - Modified `onWbModeChange`:\n   - Added `stopWbTimer()` and checkbox reset when mode === 'manual'\n   - Commented out the checkbox reset for 'local' mode (no stop needed)\n\n3. ✅ Frontend: `console.html` - Modified `onFocusModeChange`:\n   - Added `stopFocusTimer()` and checkbox reset when mode === 'manual'\n   - Commented out the checkbox reset for 'local' mode (no stop needed)\n\n4. ✅ Version: constants.py updated to v8.63\n\n5. ✅ Backup: backup_20260707_2030/ created\n\nThe modifications are complete. Now I should summarize what was done. - 1\n\nback2backendpy... a\n\nWait, I missed something. I said I'd add stopWbTimer() earlier, but I don't see it being called anywhere for 'local' mode. Let me check the changes again:\n\n```javascript\nif (mode === 'local') {\n    // ...\n    // v8.63: 局部模式下不需要停止定时器\n\n\n}\n```\n\nYes, I correctly commented out the checkbox reset for 'local' mode. This matches the boss's requirement.\n\nI've completed all the requested modifications. The backend whitebalance logic is updated to use stage thresholds instead of step-based upgrades. The frontend handles mode changes by stopping timers for 'manual' mode and not interrupting 'local' mode. The version has been incremented, and everything is backed up.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"完成。v8.63 修改总结：\n\n### 修改清单\n\n**1. 前端 console.html - 定时器停止逻辑**\n- `onWbModeChange()`: 切\"手动\"时停止白平衡定时器\n- `onFocusModeChange()`: 切\"手动\"时停止对焦定时器\n- 切\"局部\"模式 → 不停止定时器（老板要求）\n\n**2. 后端 whitebalance.py - 白平衡步进逻辑**\n- `IterativeWB.__init__()`: \n  - 移除 `_stage_min` + `_tolerances`\n  - 新增 `_stage_thresholds = [100, 10, 0.1]`\n- `step()`: \n  - 阶段升级改为 `actual <= _stage_thresholds[stage]`\n  - 精调停止改为 `fine_steps >= 20 or actual < 0.1`\n\n**3. 版本号**: v8.62 → v8.63\n\n**4. 备份**: backup_20260707_2030/\n\n### 问题1回复\n\n| 场景 | 是否停止 | 修改状态 |\n|------|----------|----------|\n| 对焦：切手动/自动 | 停止定时器 | ✅ v8.63已改 |\n| 对焦：切局部 | 不停止 | ✅ 不变 |\n| 白平衡：切手动/自动 | 停止定时器 | ✅ v8.63已改 |\n| 白平衡：切局部 | 不停止 | ✅ 不变 |\n\n### 问题2响应状态\n\n- 粗调(stage=0): 步进±5，`delta <= 100` → 进入中调\n- 中调(stage=1): 步进±2，`delta < 10` → 进入精调  \n- 精调(stage=2): 步进±1，`fine_steps >= 20` 或 `delta < 0.1` → 完成\n\n已完成精确修复，不再增加参数，基于现有逻辑重写。已备份并修复完成。若 Delta 阈值（粗调100/中调10/精调0.1）实际测试不匹配，可向我提示新的阈值范围。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":80509,"output":941,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81450,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783428068499,"responseId":"cht000d1dce@dx19f3c98c54d29c2503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"82cbb73e","parentId":"0e354247","timestamp":"2026-07-07T12:42:31.019Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"47943\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-07-07 20:42 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n按照你现在的白平衡\n1. 如果当前delta已经<100，启动多少步进，迭代多少次，取得什么结果？\n2. 如果调整过程中出现更大，比如从99到100，处理逻辑是怎么样的？"}],"timestamp":1783428151015}}
{"type":"message","id":"1b95bf73","parentId":"82cbb73e","timestamp":"2026-07-07T12:43:55.424Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板问的是两个场景：\n1. 初始 delta < 100，启动多少步进，迭代多少次，最终结果是什么？\n2. 调整过程中 delta 出现波动（从99到100），处理逻辑是什么？\n\n让我仔细分析当前代码的逻辑：\n\n当前代码：\n```python\nself._stage = 0  # 初始粗调\nself._stage_thresholds = [100, 10, 0.1]\n\ndef step(self, bgr) -> dict:\n    actual =  # delta，范围 0~2\n    \n    # 阶段升级 - 基于delta阈值\n    if self._stage < 2 and actual <= self._stage_thresholds[self._stage]:\n        self._stage += 1  # 升级到下一阶段\n```\n\n**场景1：初始 delta < 100**\n- 初始 `_stage = 0`（粗调），`actual < 100`\n- 检查投影条件：`self._stage < 2`（True）&& `actual <= _stage_thresholds[0]`（即 `actual <= 100`）\n- 条件满足 → 立即 `self._stage += 1` → `_stage = 1`（中调）\n- 然后返回 continue，step_size = 2（中调步进）\n\n所以：\n1. 启动步进：第1次调用时，step_size = 5（粗调），但立即升级到中调\n2. 迭代次数：第1步就开始升级，所以仍然是 ±5 步进，但 stage 指示为 \"medium\"\n我继续分析最终结果：\n3. 迭代阶段：从第1步开始就直接进入中调阶段，可能不会执行完整的粗调优化路径\n4. 搜索策略：系统会尝试 ±2 步进调整，但由于步骤阈值已满足，可能不会进行多次迭代\n\n**场景2：delta 波动测试**\n我注意到一个小错误需要修正——当前不应立即读取 `_stage_thresholds`，而是应该将其移到 `__init__` 方法中初始化。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"老板提出的关键问题，让我详细回答当前实现的实际行为："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4c3359171a9d49eb89d38726","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\controlpanel\\whitebalance.py","offset":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":81647,"output":510,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82157,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783428151019,"responseId":"cht000daae9@dx19f3c9a6bc62872503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6190cc9d","parentId":"1b95bf73","timestamp":"2026-07-07T12:43:55.437Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_4c3359171a9d49eb89d38726","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# ─────────────────────────────────────────────\n\nclass IterativeWB:\n    \"\"\"白平衡迭代搜索器 - R/B 独立调整\n    \n    状态：粗调(±5) → 中调(±2) → 精调(±1)\n    每步评估 [双通道, 仅R, 仅B] 三个候选，选 delta 最小。\n    全程追踪 best_gains + best_delta，结束时回滚到最佳。\n    \n    输入：BGR图像\n    输出：dict（action, red_gain, blue_gain, delta, message等）\n    \n    不涉及任何设备操作，纯粹数学逻辑。\n    \"\"\"\n\n    def __init__(self, current_red=100, current_blue=100):\n        self._stage = 0\n        self._stage_steps = [5, 2, 1]\n        # v8.63: 阶段升级阈值 - 粗调delta<=100, 中调delta<10, 精调delta<0.1\n        self._stage_thresholds = [100, 10, 0.1]\n        self._current_red = current_red\n        self._current_blue = current_blue\n        self._no_improve = 0\n        self._stage_step_count = 0\n        self._fine_steps = 0\n        self._best_red = current_red\n        self._best_blue = current_blue\n        self._best_delta = 999.0\n        self._best_step = 0\n        self._step_count = 0\n\n[315 more lines in file. Use offset=45 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783428235437}}
{"type":"message","id":"b716b62b","parentId":"6190cc9d","timestamp":"2026-07-07T12:44:03.166Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_75674d688fb7401da4e1f229","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"offset":95,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\controlpanel\\whitebalance.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":82199,"output":48,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82247,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783428235439,"responseId":"cht000db981@dx19f3c9b512c2872503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"04592464","parentId":"b716b62b","timestamp":"2026-07-07T12:44:03.171Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_75674d688fb7401da4e1f229","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            self._best_delta = actual\n            self._best_red = self._current_red\n            self._best_blue = self._current_blue\n            self._best_step = self._step_count\n\n        # 无改善计数\n        tolerance = 0.95  # v8.63: 统一容忍度\n        if actual >= prev_best * tolerance:\n            self._no_improve += 1\n        else:\n            self._no_improve = 0\n\n        stage_name = [\"coarse\", \"medium\", \"fine\"][self._stage]\n\n        # v8.63: 阶段升级 - 基于delta阈值\n        # 粗调→中调: delta <= 100\n        # 中调→精调: delta < 10\n        if self._stage < 2 and actual <= self._stage_thresholds[self._stage]:\n            self._stage += 1\n            self._stage_step_count = 0\n            self._no_improve = 0\n            # 进入精调时重置best追踪\n            if self._stage == 2:\n                self._best_delta = 999.0\n                self._best_red = self._current_red\n                self._best_blue = self._current_blue\n                self._best_step = self._step_count\n            return {\n                \"action\": \"continue\",\n                \"stage\": [\"medium\", \"fine\"][self._stage - 1],\n                \"step_size\": self._stage_steps[self._stage],\n                \"red_gain\": self._current_red, \"blue_gain\": self._current_blue,\n                \"r_avg\": round(stats[\"r_avg\"], 1), \"g_avg\": round(stats[\"g_avg\"], 1), \"b_avg\": round(stats[\"b_avg\"], 1),\n                \"delta\": round(actual, 4), \"best_delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"pixels\": n,\n                \"message\": f\"进入{'中等' if self._stage == 1 else '精细'}调校 (step=±{self._stage_steps[self._stage]})\"\n            }\n\n        # 精调阶段处理 - 上限20步或delta<0.1\n        if self._stage == 2:\n            self._fine_steps += 1\n            if self._fine_steps >= 20 or actual < 0.1:\n                rollback = (self._best_red != self._current_red or self._best_blue != self._current_blue)\n                self._current_red = self._best_red\n                self._current_blue = self._best_blue\n                return {\n                    \"action\": \"stop\",\n                    \"stage\": \"done\",\n                    \"step_size\": 0,\n                    \"red_gain\": self._best_red, \"blue_gain\": self._best_blue,\n                    \"r_avg\": round(stats[\"r_avg\"], 1), \"g_avg\": round(stats[\"g_avg\"], 1), \"b_avg\": round(stats[\"b_avg\"], 1),\n                    \"delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"best_delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"pixels\": n,\n                    \"message\": f\"白平衡完成 {'(回滚至最佳)' if rollback else '(已达最佳)'} 第{self._best_step}步\"\n                }\n\n        # 应用新增益\n        self._current_red = new_red\n        self._current_blue = new_blue\n        return {\n            \"action\": \"continue\",\n            \"stage\": stage_name,\n            \"step_size\": step,\n            \"red_gain\": new_red, \"blue_gain\": new_blue,\n            \"r_avg\": round(stats[\"r_avg\"], 1), \"g_avg\": round(stats[\"g_avg\"], 1), \"b_avg\": round(stats[\"b_avg\"], 1),\n            \"delta\": round(actual, 4), \"best_delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"pixels\": n,\n            \"message\": f\"{'粗' if self._stage == 0 else '中' if self._stage == 1 else '精'}调 {direction} (±{step})\"\n        }\n\n\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────\n# 执行层：协调设备操作\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────\n\nclass WhiteBalanceSearcher:\n    \"\"\"白平衡搜索执行器\n    \n    负责：\n    - 切换手动白平衡模式\n    - 读取当前增益\n    - 截取框选区域\n    - 调用IterativeWB.step()\n    - 应用增益到设备\n    - 切换锁定白平衡模式\n    - 验证结果\n    - 产生SSE事件\n    \n    不做任何算法决策，只执行。\n    \"\"\"\n    \n    def __init__(self, mgr, device_ip, client, x, y, w, h, capture_func, cleanup_func, mac_clean=\"\"):\n        self.mgr = mgr\n        self.device_ip = device_ip\n        self.client = client\n        self.x = x\n        self.y = y\n        self.w = w\n        self.h = h\n        self._capture_func = capture_func\n        self._cleanup_func = cleanup_func\n        self._interrupted = False  # v8.41: 中断标志\n        self._mac_clean = mac_clean  # v8.47: 用于保存设置\n\n[165 more lines in file. Use offset=195 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783428243171}}
{"type":"message","id":"7f9e4754","parentId":"04592464","timestamp":"2026-07-07T12:44:19.811Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在我完全理解了代码逻辑。让我回答老板的两个问题。\n\n## 问题1：初始 delta < 100\n\n当前 `actual` 的范围是 `abs(r/g - 1) + abs(b/g - 1)`，通常 0~2。\n\n**第一步执行流程**：\n1. `_stage = 0`（粗调），`step = 5`\n2. 计算候选增益，选最优\n3. 计算 `actual`（假设 = 0.5）\n4. 更新 best（首次必更新）\n5. 阶段升级检查：`self._stage < 2` ✅ && `actual(0.5) <= _stage_thresholds[0](100)` ✅\n6. **立即升级** → `_stage = 1`（中调）\n7. 返回 `action: continue, stage: medium, step_size: 2`\n8. **不应用新增益**，直接返回当前值\n\n**问题**：\n- 第1步没有实际调整增益，只是\"升级\"了阶段\n- `actual` 几乎永远 <= 100（范围0~2），所以粗调阶段**第1步就跳过**了\n- 同理，`actual <= 10` 也几乎永远满足，中调第1步也跳过\n- 直接进入精调(stage=2)，步进 ±1，最多20步或 `actual < 0.1`\n\n**结论**：粗调和中调形同虚设，直接进入精调。\n\n## 问题2：delta 从 99 到 100\n\n**不会出现**。因为 `actual` 的数学范围是 0~2，不可能达到 99 或 100。\n\n但假设老板说的 delta 是另一个含义（比如百分比），从 99 变到 100：\n- 阶段升级条件：`actual <= _stage_thresholds[stage]`\n- 如果之前 `actual=99`（已满足 <=100，已升级到中调）\n- 现在 `actual=100`（仍满足 <=100，但已在 stage=1）\n- 中调升级条件：`actual <= 10` — 100 > 10，不升级\n- 继续中调步进 ±2\n\n**问题**：delta 波动时，没有回退机制。`_no_improve` 计数存在但**不用于阶段升级判断**，只用于统计。`best` 追踪会记录最优值，但不会主动回退。\n\n---\n\n## 核心问题\n\n**`actual` 的范围是 0~2，老板说的阈值 100/10/0.1 与实际值不在同一个量级。**\n\n需要老板确认：delta 的定义是否需要修改？还是阈值需要调整？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":83392,"output":582,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83974,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783428243173,"responseId":"cht000d37dc@dx19f3c9b69ae2871503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"348476d5","parentId":"7f9e4754","timestamp":"2026-07-07T12:49:21.999Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"47947\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-07-07 20:49 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n不是，我的问题是，从步进5调整，下降到99了，但是下一次调整从99变成了101，也就是上升了，此时应该用多少的步进？"}],"timestamp":1783428561995}}
{"type":"message","id":"5c3351bf","parentId":"348476d5","timestamp":"2026-07-07T12:50:16.830Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板的问题很明确：\n\n**场景**：粗调阶段，步进±5\n- 第N步：delta = 99（已满足 <=100）\n- 第N+1步：delta = 101（又超出100了）\n\n**问题**：此时应该用多少步进？\n\n让我看当前代码的逻辑：\n\n```python\n# 阶段升级检查\nif self._stage < 2 and actual <= self._stage_thresholds[self._stage]:\n    self._stage += 1  # 升级\n    return ...  # 返回，不应用新增益\n```\n\n当前逻辑：\n1. delta=99 时，`actual(99) <= 100` → 升级到中调(stage=1)\n2. 下一步进入中调，步进变为 ±2\n3. 但设备实际还没调整（上一步升级时没应用新增益）\n4. 重新截图后 delta 可能波动到 101\n\n**问题**：已经升级到中调(stage=1)了，但 delta 又超过100了。中调的升级条件是 `actual <= 10`，101 > 10，所以不会升级，继续用中调步进 ±2。\n\n但这里的问题是：**delta=101 时应该用粗调 ±5 还是中调 ±2？**\n\n老板的意思是：delta 波动时，应该根据当前 delta 值决定步进，而不是根据已升级的阶段。\n\n也就是说，阶段不应该是\"只升不降\"的，而应该根据当前 delta 值动态决定：\n- delta > 100 → 粗调 ±5\n- 10 < delta <= 100 → 中调 ±2\n- delta <= 10 → 精调 ±1\n\n这是**动态阶段选择**，不是**阶段升级**。\n\n当前代码是\"单向升级\"：一旦升级到中调，即使 delta 回到 101，仍然用中调步进 ±2。\n\n老板要求的是\"动态选择\"：每一步根据当前 delta 值决定步进大小。\n\n这就简单了 — 不需要\"阶段升级\"逻辑，每步直接根据 delta 值选择步进。\n\n这是一个很简洁的修改思路。\n\n老板问的是：delta 从 99 变成 101（上升了），此时应该用多少步进？\n\n**当前代码**：已经升级到中调，步进 ±2，不会降级回粗调。\n\n**老板期望**：delta=101 > 100，应该回到粗调步进 ±5。\n\n修改方案：将\"阶段升级\"改为\"动态阶段选择\"，每步根据 delta 值决定步进。\n\n但老板只问了问题，没有让我修改。让我直接回答。\n\n老板，明白了。\n\n**当前代码的问题**：阶段是**只升不降**的。delta=99 时升级到中调(±2)，下一步 delta=101 仍然用中调 ±2。\n\n**正确逻辑应该是**：每步根据当前 delta **动态选择**步进：\n- delta > 100 → ±5\n- 10 < delta <= 100 → ±2\n- delta <= 10 → ±1\n\n不需要\"阶段升级\"机制，每步独立判断。需要改吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":84163,"output":676,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84839,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783428561999,"responseId":"cht000d290e@dx19f3ca0ddc929bb503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e856888a","parentId":"5c3351bf","timestamp":"2026-07-07T12:54:59.870Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"47950\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-07-07 20:54 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n现在单向调整步进的方法是正确的，但是我需要你调整阈值\n步进5的阈值是>=10，步进2的阈值是>=1，步进1是<1。\n另外，检查现在整个白平衡过程中，每一步调整，有多少次操作设备、截图这类和设备交互的动作，分析频次，目前还是出现截图失败，应该是有高频访问，我要在不修改业务逻辑的情况下，给我找出降低频次的方案\n检查之后给我调整计划"}],"timestamp":1783428899866}}
{"type":"message","id":"f1ceb953","parentId":"e856888a","timestamp":"2026-07-07T12:55:25.158Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板要求两件事：1. 调整白平衡步进阈值：   - 步进±5：delta >= 10   - 步进±2：delta >= 1\n   - 步进±1：delta < 1   注意：这里不再是\"升级阈值\"，而是\"当前delta所在区间决定步进\"。但老板说\"单向调整步进的方法是正确的\"，所以仍然是只升不降的阶段升级。   等等，让我重新理解。老板说\"单向调整步进的方法是正确的\"，意味着阶段只升不降。但阈值变了：   - 粗调(stage=0)：步进±5，升级条件是 delta <= 10（注意老板说\">=10\"是粗调的条件，即delta>=10时用步进5，delta<=10时升级）      等等，老板说的是\"步进5的阈值是>=10\"，意思是delta >= 10时用步进5。\"步进2的阈值是>=1\"，delta >= 1且 < 10时用步进2。\"步进1是<1\"，delta < 1时用步进1。   但老板又说\"单向调整步进的方法是正确的\"，即只升不降。   所以升级条件：   - 粗调→中调：delta < 10（从 >=10 降到 <10）   - 中调→精调：delta < 1（从 >=1 降到 <1）   精调停止：delta < 0.1 或 20步上限？   等等，老板之前说的精调停止条件是\"上限20步，或者直到获得0.1以内的delta\"。   但现在老板说\"步进1是<1\"，意思是delta < 1时进入精调。精调的停止条件呢？   老板之前说\"精调(stage=2): 步进 ±1，上限20步，或者直到获得0.1以内的delta\"。   所以：   - 粗调(stage=0)：步进±5，delta < 10 时升级到中调   - 中调(stage=1)：步进±2，delta < 1 时升级到精调   - 精调(stage=2)：步进±1，delta < 0.1 或 20步上限时停止   阈值数组：_stage_thresholds = [10, 1, 0.1]   2. 分析白平衡过程中每步的设备交互频次，找出降低频次的方案   让我分析 WhiteBalanceSearcher.run() 中的设备交互：   每一步循环中：\n   1. wb.step(bgr) — 纯算法，无设备交互\n   2. 如果 cmd[\"action\"] == \"stop\":      a. _set_wb_gains(red, blue) — 1次PUT      b. calc_stable_delay(client) — 1次GET（读取曝光参数）      c. _capture() — 1次GET（截图）      d. _set_wb_mode(\"locked\") — 1次PUT      e. _cleanup_func() — 1次调用   3. 如果 cmd[\"action\"] == \"continue\":\n      a. _set_wb_gains(red, blue) — 1次PUT      b. calc_stable_delay(client) — 1次GET      c. _capture() — 1次GET（截图）      还有循环开始时的中断检查：   - 如果中断：_set_wb_gains() — 1次PUT, calc_stable_delay() — 1次GET, _set_wb_mode(\"locked\") — 1次PUT   初始化阶段：\n   1. _read_wb_status() — 1次GET   2. _set_wb_mode(\"manual\") — 1次PUT   3. 如果auto模式：_set_wb_gains(50, 50) — 1次PUT   4. _capture() — 1次GET（初始截图）   每步常规操作：\n   - _set_wb_gains() — 1次PUT（设置增益）   - calc_stable_delay() — 1次GET（读取曝光参数计算延迟）   - sleep(delay) — 等待   - _capture() — 1次GET（截图）   = 每步3次设备交互 + 1次等待   让我看看 calc_stable_delay 的实现：   需要读取 region_base.py 中的 calc_stable_delay 函数。   另外，_capture 函数实际调用 _capture_and_crop，让我看看这个函数做了什么。   让我检查这些函数的实现。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"先分析阈值调整，再检查设备交互频次。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_40431b973e3244e1a8cca66c","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\controlpanel\\region_base.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":85091,"output":1058,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86149,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783428899870,"responseId":"cht000d5df5@dx19f3ca574e32872503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"fff21356","parentId":"f1ceb953","timestamp":"2026-07-07T12:55:25.168Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_40431b973e3244e1a8cca66c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"AstroHub v8.60 - 画面分析基础工具\n\n提供：\n- _valid_pixels() - 排除死黑(0,0,0)和死白(255,255,255)的像素\n- _rgb_stats() - 计算RGB统计信息\n- calc_contrast() - 计算反差值（Laplacian方差的float）\n- get_exposure_time() - 获取曝光时间（固定1/25，检查慢快门）\n- calc_stable_delay() - 计算稳定延时 = 基础延迟1.5s + 慢快门额外时间\n\"\"\"\n\nimport cv2\nimport numpy as np\n\n\ndef _valid_pixels(bgr: np.ndarray):\n    \"\"\"排除死黑(0,0,0)和死白(255,255,255)，返回(B, G, R)三通道有效像素数组和计数。\"\"\"\n    dead_black = np.all(bgr == 0, axis=2)\n    dead_white = np.all(bgr == 255, axis=2)\n    valid = ~(dead_black | dead_white)\n    n = np.count_nonzero(valid)\n    if n < 10:\n        return None, None, None, None, 0\n    return bgr[:, :, 0][valid], bgr[:, :, 1][valid], bgr[:, :, 2][valid], valid, n\n\n\ndef _rgb_stats(bgr: np.ndarray) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"计算框选区域有效像素的RGB统计。\"\"\"\n    b_ch, g_ch, r_ch, _, n = _valid_pixels(bgr)\n    b_sum, g_sum, r_sum = float(b_ch.sum()), float(g_ch.sum()), float(r_ch.sum())\n    b_avg, g_avg, r_avg = float(b_ch.mean()), float(g_ch.mean()), float(r_ch.mean())\n    return {\n        \"n\": n,\n        \"b_sum\": b_sum,\n        \"g_sum\": g_sum,\n        \"r_sum\": r_sum,\n        \"b_avg\": b_avg,\n        \"g_avg\": g_avg,\n        \"r_avg\": r_avg\n    }\n\n\ndef calc_contrast(bgr: np.ndarray) -> float:\n    \"\"\"计算框选区域的反差值（Laplacian方差）。\"\"\"\n    gray = cv2.cvtColor(bgr, cv2.COLOR_BGR2GRAY)\n    return float(cv2.Laplacian(gray, cv2.CV_64F).var())\n\n\ndef _parse_shutter_level(level_str: str) -> float:\n    \"\"\"解析快门值字符串为秒数。\"\"\"\n    try:\n        level_str = level_str.strip()\n        if \"/\" in level_str:\n            num, den = level_str.split(\"/\")\n            return float(num) / float(den)\n        return float(level_str)\n    except (ValueError, ZeroDivisionError):\n        return 0.04\n\n\ndef get_exposure_time(client) -> float:\n    \"\"\"获取慢快门额外曝光时间（秒）。\n\n    基础快门 1/25=0.04s。检查慢快门是否开启。\n    返回慢快门额外时间（无慢快门返回0）。\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/Shutter\")\n        if resp.status_code != 200:\n            return 0.0\n\n        import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n        root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\n\n        min_limit = None\n        max_limit = None\n\n        for elem in root.iter():\n            tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\n            if tag in (\"minShutterLevelLimit\", \"MinShutterLevelLimit\"):\n                min_limit = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\n            elif tag in (\"maxShutterLevelLimit\", \"MaxShutterLevelLimit\"):\n                max_limit = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\n\n        if min_limit and max_limit and min_limit != max_limit:\n            min_time = _parse_shutter_level(min_limit)\n            max_time = _parse_shutter_level(max_limit)\n            if min_time > 0 and max_time > min_time:\n                return max_time - min_time\n\n        return 0.0\n    except Exception:\n        return 0.0\n\n\ndef calc_stable_delay(client) -> float:\n    \"\"\"计算操作后的稳定延时。\n\n    公式: 固定1.5s + 1/25 × 慢快门倍率（如果有）\n    \"\"\"\n    slow_extra = get_exposure_time(client)\n    return 1.5 + slow_extra\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783428925168}}
