{"type":"message","id":"1ce57fc5","parentId":"df38146f","timestamp":"2026-07-07T13:17:04.291Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_fc8ce9ec953b480daa5ca40c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        // 2. 白平衡 R/B - v7.55: 只显示数值\r\n        apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/whitebalance').then(function(r) {\r\n            if (r && r.success && r.data) {\r\n                var wb = r.data;\r\n                var rEl = document.getElementById('ptzWbR');\r\n                var bEl = document.getElementById('ptzWbB');\r\n                if (rEl) rEl.textContent = wb.red_gain || '--';\r\n                if (bEl) bEl.textContent = wb.blue_gain || '--';\r\n            }\r\n        }).catch(function(e) {});\r\n\r\n        // 3. 降噪空域/时域 - v7.55: 只显示数值\r\n        apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/noisereduce').then(function(r) {\r\n            if (r && r.success && r.data) {\r\n                var nr = r.data;\r\n                var sEl = document.getElementById('ptzDnrSpatial');\r\n                var tEl = document.getElementById('ptzDnrTemporal');\r\n                var spatialVal = (nr.spatial_level !== undefined && nr.spatial_level !== null) ? nr.spatial_level : '--';\r\n                var temporalVal = (nr.temporal_level !== undefined && nr.temporal_level !== null) ? nr.temporal_level : '--';\r\n                if (sEl) sEl.textContent = spatialVal;\r\n                if (tEl) tEl.textContent = temporalVal;\r\n            }\r\n        }).catch(function(e) {});\r\n\r\n        // 4. 光圈 - v8.58: 显示F-num格式 (如: F2.0表示f/2.0)\r\n        apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/iris').then(function(r) {\r\n            if (r && r.success && r.data) {\r\n                var ir = r.data;\r\n                var iEl = document.getElementById('ptzIris');\r\n                if (iEl) {\r\n                    var level = ir.current_level;\r\n                    if (level !== undefined && level !== null) {\r\n                        iEl.textContent = 'F' + (level / 100).toFixed(1);  // 如: 200 → F2.0\r\n                    } else {\r\n                        iEl.textContent = '--';\r\n                    }\r\n                }\r\n            }\r\n        }).catch(function(e) {});\r\n\r\n        // 5. 快门 - v7.55: 只显示数值\r\n        apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/shutter').then(function(r) {\r\n            if (r && r.success && r.data) {\r\n                var sh = r.data;\r\n                var sEl = document.getElementById('ptzShutter');\r\n                if (sEl) sEl.textContent = sh.current_level || '--';\r\n            }\r\n        }).catch(function(e) {});\r\n    }, 1000);\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction stopPtzImagePoll() {\r\n    if (_ptzImagePollInterval) {\r\n        clearInterval(_ptzImagePollInterval);\r\n        _ptzImagePollInterval = null;\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 暴露到全局\r\nwindow.startPtzImagePoll = startPtzImagePoll;\r\nwindow.stopPtzImagePoll = stopPtzImagePoll;\r\n\r\n// ==================== 暴露到全局 ====================\r\nwindow.toggleSection = toggleSection;\r\nwindow.loadDeviceImageParams = loadDeviceImageParams;\r\nwindow.setSharpness = setSharpness;\r\nwindow.setWhiteBalanceMode = setWhiteBalanceMode;\r\nwindow.setWhiteBalanceGain = setWhiteBalanceGain;\r\nwindow.setNoiseReduce = setNoiseReduce;\r\nwindow.loadFilterStatus = loadFilterStatus;\r\nwindow.setDayNightMode = setDayNightMode;\r\nwindow.setShutterSpeed = setShutterSpeed;\r\nwindow.setIris = setIris;\r\nwindow.setExposureMode = setExposureMode;\r\nwindow.togglePtzOsd = togglePtzOsd;\r\nwindow.toggleInfoOsd = toggleInfoOsd;\r\nwindow.updatePtzOsdButtons = updatePtzOsdButtons;\r\nwindow.updateInfoOsdButtons = updateInfoOsdButtons;\r\nwindow.setSlowShutter = setSlowShutter;\r\nwindow.loadSlowShutter = loadSlowShutter;\r\n// v7.32: 新增功能检测相关函数\r\nwindow.goToFunctionTest = goToFunctionTest;\r\nwindow.showFunctionOverlay = showFunctionOverlay;\r\nwindow.removeFunctionOverlay = removeFunctionOverlay;\r\n// v8.38: 白平衡/对焦模式切换 + 停止函数\r\nwindow.onWbModeChange = onWbModeChange;\r\nwindow.onFocusModeChange = onFocusModeChange;\r\nwindow.stopAutoWhiteBalance = stopAutoWhiteBalance;\r\nwindow.stopAutoFocus = stopAutoFocus;\r\n// v8.58: consoleSnapshot函数已移至console.html单独定义\r\nwindow.consoleSnapshot = consoleSnapshot;\r\n</script>\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783430224291}}
{"type":"message","id":"36de3548","parentId":"1ce57fc5","timestamp":"2026-07-07T13:18:20.134Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在让我整理分析结果：\n\n**主控台轮询（startPtzImagePoll，1秒一次）**：\n1. GET /api/v1/ptz/{dev}/position (PTZ坐标)\n2. GET /api/v1/ptz/{dev}/image/whitebalance (R/B)\n3. GET /api/v1/ptz/{dev}/image/noisereduce (降噪)  \n4. GET /api/v1/ptz/{dev}/image/iris (光圈)\n5. GET /api/v1/ptz/{dev}/image/shutter (快门)\n\n**白平衡搜索（每步）**：\n1. PUT /Image/channels/1/whiteBalance (设置R/B)\n2. _capture_and_crop():\n   a. calc_stable_delay(client) → GET /Image/channels/1/Shutter\n   b. sleep(delay)\n   c. client.capture_picture() → GET /ISAPI/Streaming/Channels/1/picture\n\nrun() 中的逻辑：\n1. _set_wb_mode(\"manual\") 或 _set_wb_mode(\"locked\")\n2. _set_wb_gains() → PUT /Image/channels/1/whiteBalance\n3. calc_stable_delay(client) → GET /Image/channels/1/Shutter\n4. sleep(delay)\n5. _capture() → 调用 _capture_and_crop() → 重复调用 calc_stable_delay + sleep\n6. sleep(delay) ← 又一次\n\n所以每步设备交互：\n1. PUT /Image/channels/1/whiteBalance\n\n\n2. GET /Image/channels/1/Shutter - 2次（重复）\n3. GET /ISAPI/Streaming/Channels/1/picture - 1次\n4. sleep - 2次\n\n搜索总耗时约3秒，具体取决于稳定延迟和截图过程。每次搜索循环都会产生多次重复的HTTP请求和系统资源消耗。高频率的设备交互可能导致性能瓶颈和潜在的截图失败问题。\n\n为解决这个问题，建议采取针对性优化策略。首先，暂停轮询机制可以显著减少干扰。其次，通过共享延时参数避免重复的GET请求和sleep操作。最后，缓存快门值可以进一步降低资源开销。这些方法旨在提高搜索过程的效率和稳定性。\n\n我注意到可能存在重复的 HTTP 请求，特别是在主控台轮询和白平衡设置过程中可能因为时间接近而同时发送请求。这种情况下，还需要考虑端点响应速度和设备负载等因素。\n\n为了降低请求频次，我建议先暂停主控台轮询方案。优化 _capture_and_crop() 函数，通过增加 skip_delay 参数来避免重复等待。这种方案相对简单，如果存在截图失败，可能需要进一步排查设备低压或网络延迟问题。\n\n接下来需要准备后续的优化方案和调整计划。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"好的，让我继续分析，给老板完整的优化方案。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fa431aa7b5a24bfe823ffcd0","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":80,"offset":810,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":91927,"output":647,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92574,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783430224292,"responseId":"cht000d4431@dx19f3cb9ae0c29c2503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"bd697606","parentId":"36de3548","timestamp":"2026-07-07T13:18:20.140Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_fa431aa7b5a24bfe823ffcd0","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"async def get_connected_device() -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"v7.10: 获取当前连接状态和上次连接设备信息。\r\n\r\n    返回:\r\n    - connected: 当前是否已连接(基于 active_device)\r\n    - device: 上次连接的设备信息(基于 last_connected,用于快速连接)\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    import json\r\n    from src.config_paths import REGISTRY_FILE\r\n\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")  # type: ignore[assignment]\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\", \"connected\": False, \"device\": None}\r\n\r\n    # v7.10: 获取上次连接的设备(用于快速连接)\r\n    device = mgr.get_connected_device()\r\n\r\n    # v7.10: 检查当前是否实际连接(基于 active_device)\r\n    # v7.31: 同时检查 active_device 非空 AND _controllers 非空\r\n    connected = False\r\n    try:\r\n        if REGISTRY_FILE.exists():\r\n            registry = json.loads(REGISTRY_FILE.read_text(encoding='utf-8'))\r\n            active_mac = registry.get('active_device', '').strip()\r\n            # 同时检查 active_device 非空 AND 实际连接存在\r\n            if active_mac and hasattr(mgr, '_controllers') and mgr._controllers:\r\n                connected = True\r\n    except Exception:\r\n        pass\r\n\r\n    if not device:\r\n        return {\"success\": True, \"connected\": False, \"device\": None}\r\n\r\n    return {\"success\": True, \"connected\": connected, \"device\": device}\r\n\r\n@api_router.get(\"/system/info\", summary=\"系统硬件信息 (P1.1)\", tags=[\"System\"])\r\nasync def get_system_info() -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"获取本机系统硬件信息 (hostname/CPU/RAM/GPU/VRAM)。\"\"\"\r\n    try:\r\n        from src.ptz.core.system_info import collect_system_info\r\n        info = collect_system_info()\r\n        return {\"success\": True, \"data\": info}\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": str(e)}\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.get(\"/system/nics\", summary=\"网络接口列表 (P1.2)\", tags=[\"System\"])\r\nasync def get_nics() -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"获取所有网络接口列表,按优先级排序。\"\"\"\r\n    try:\r\n        from src.core.net_detector import get_all_nics\r\n        nics = get_all_nics()\r\n        return {\"success\": True, \"data\": nics, \"total\": len(nics)}\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": str(e)}\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.get(\"/system/default-ip\", summary=\"推荐目标 IP (P1.3)\", tags=[\"System\"])\r\nasync def get_default_ip() -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"获取推荐的目标 IP 地址。\"\"\"\r\n    try:\r\n        from src.core.net_detector import suggest_target_ip\r\n        ip = suggest_target_ip()\r\n        return {\"success\": True, \"data\": {\"ip\": ip}}\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": str(e)}\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.get(\"/system/operations\", summary=\"操作日志 (最近10条)\", tags=[\"System\"])\r\nasync def get_operations_log() -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"获取最近 10 条操作日志。\"\"\"\r\n    return {\"success\": True, \"data\": list(reversed(operations_log)), \"total\": len(operations_log)}\r\n\r\n\r\n@health_router.get(\"/log/operations/file\", summary=\"从文件读取操作日志\")\r\nasync def get_operation_log_file(lines: int = 50) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"从日志文件读取最近N条操作日志.\"\"\"\r\n    from src.operation_logger import LOG_DIR\r\n    from datetime import datetime\r\n\r\n\n[3430 more lines in file. Use offset=890 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783430300140}}
{"type":"message","id":"5f03810d","parentId":"bd697606","timestamp":"2026-07-07T13:19:16.528Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在我完全理解了整个链路。让我给老板精简的分析和方案。\n\n## 设备交互频次分析\n\n### 后台轮询（持续运行，1次/秒）\n| # | 请求 | 端点 |\n|---|------|------|\n| 1 | PTZ坐标 | GET /ptz/{dev}/position |\n| 2 | 白平衡R/B | GET /ptz/{dev}/image/whitebalance |\n| 3 | 降噪 | GET /ptz/{dev}/image/noisereduce |\n| 4 | 光圈 | GET /ptz/{dev}/image/iris |\n| 5 | 快门 | GET /ptz/{dev}/image/shutter |\n\n**= 5次/秒**\n\n### 白平衡搜索每步\n| # | 请求 | 端点 | 来源 |\n|---|------|------|------|\n| 1 | 设置R/B | PUT /Image/channels/1/whiteBalance | run() |\n| 2 | 读Shutter | GET /Image/channels/1/Shutter | run() 中 calc_stable_delay |\n| 3 | sleep | — | run() |\n| 4 | 读Shutter | GET /Image/channels/1/Shutter | _capture_and_crop() 中 calc_stable_delay **← 重复** |\n| 5 | sleep | — | _capture_and_crop() **← 重复** |\n| 6 | 截图 | GET /ISAPI/Streaming/Channels/1/picture | _capture_and_crop() |\n\n**= 4次设备交互 + 2次sleep（其中各1次重复）**\n\n### 叠加频次\n- 每步耗时 ≈ 2×1.5s sleep + 截图 ≈ 3.5s\n- 期间后台轮询：5次/秒 × 3.5s ≈ **17次**\n- 搜索本身：**4次**\n- **总计每步 ≈ 21次设备交互**\n\n---\n\n## 优化方案（不修改业务逻辑）\n\n### 优化1：搜索期间暂停后台轮询\n**文件**: `console.html`\n**修改**: `executeScheduledSearch()` 和手动搜索开始时调用 `stopPtzImagePoll()`，结束后调用 `startPtzImagePoll()`\n**效果**: 每步减少 ~17次GET\n**复用**: `stopPtzImagePoll()` / `startPtzImagePoll()` 已有\n\n### 优化2：消除 _capture_and_crop 中的重复 calc_stable_delay\n**文件**: `router.py` — `_capture_and_crop()` 加 `skip_delay=False` 参数\n**文件**: `whitebalance.py` — `_capture` 调用时传 `skip_delay=True`\n**效果**: 每步减少 1次GET + 1次sleep\n**逻辑**: run() 已经 calc_stable_delay + sleep，截图前不需要再等\n\n### 优化3：缓存 Shutter 值\n**文件**: `whitebalance.py` — `WhiteBalanceSearcher` 初始化时读一次 Shutter，后续 calc_stable_delay 复用缓存值\n**效果**: 每步减少 1次GET\n**逻辑**: 白平衡搜索期间快门不会变\n\n### 优化后每步\n| # | 请求 | 来源 |\n|---|------|------|\n| 1 | PUT whiteBalance | run() |\n| 2 | ~~GET Shutter~~ | ~~缓存~~ |\n| 3 | sleep | run() |\n| 4 | ~~GET Shutter~~ | ~~skip_delay~~ |\n| 5 | ~~sleep~~ | ~~skip_delay~~ |\n| 6 | GET picture | 截图 |\n\n**= 2次设备交互 + 1次sleep（从21次降到2次）**\n\n### 阈值调整\n```\n_stage_thresholds: [100, 10, 0.1] → [10, 1, 0.1]\n```\n- 粗调→中调：delta < 10\n- 中调→精调：delta < 1\n- 精调停止：delta < 0.1 或 20步\n\n需要开始修复吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":93079,"output":898,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93977,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783430300142,"responseId":"cht000d4cd5@dx19f3cbb44112871503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"27467bff","parentId":"5f03810d","timestamp":"2026-07-07T15:02:32.667Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"47960\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-07-07 23:02 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n你这样修改之后，怎么根据快门时间动态调整截图分析的延迟？"}],"timestamp":1783436552663}}
{"type":"message","id":"1be0b872","parentId":"27467bff","timestamp":"2026-07-07T15:04:07.613Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板问的问题很关键：优化后的逻辑是：\n1. `run()` 开始时读取一次 Shutter 值\n2. 之后 calc_stable_delay 直接用缓存的 Shutter，不再每次都读\n3. `_capture_and_crop()` 被绕过（skip_delay=True），不再有 sleep\n\n但是！不太清楚老板担心的点是什么。让我重新理一下逻辑：\n\n**当前逻辑（每步）**：\n```python\n# 都用 Shutter 或延迟计算\ndelay1 = calc_stable_delay(client)  # 1次GET Shutter, 1次sleep\nsleep(delay1)\n_capture_and_crop(client, ...)  # 又1次GET Shutter, 又1次sleep\n```\n\n**优化后（每步）**：\n```python\n# 都用缓存的 Shutter\n_delay_cached = calc_stable_delay(client)  # 1次GET Shutter, 缓存\nsleep(_delay_cached)\n_capture_and_crop(client, skip_delay=True, ...)  # 不再读 Shutter, 不再sleep\n```\n\n老板可能担心的是：如果搜索期间快门变了怎么办？\n\n场景：搜索到第5步时，用户手动调了快门（从 1/25 变到 1/30）\n\n当前逻辑：\n- 第5步：读 Shutter = 1/30，计算 delay，返回白平衡\n- 当搜索结束时：\n  - 之前设置了 R/B 值\n  - 现在设备快门已经变成 1/30，不是 1/25\n- 问题：白平衡的收敛判断依赖快门值，如果快门变了，判断可能不准\n\n我意识到用户可能误解了机制。calc_stable_delay 确实动态获取快门，只缓存一次读值。除非快门发生实际变化，否则缓存不会影响后续延迟计算。关键是要确保快门值是当前的，而不是静态记录的。 操作延时与图像质量间的平衡需要谨慎。设备快门变化确实会导致计算延时不能准确匹配实时状态，但这种不匹配通常在 ±0.02秒内可接受。\n\n优化方案的核心是确保抓图操作被完整执行，不能直接绕过 sleep。通过复用延时并减少重复调用，可以高效处理图像稳定延迟。关键在于保持流程闭环，同时最小化不必要的等待。\n\n实现策略是在抓图前直接使用已计算的延迟时间，通过 skip_delay=True 是一种实用且高效的方法。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"老板这个问题问得好。\n\n## 理解老板的担心\n\n**场景**：白平衡搜索期间（假设需要10步），用户手动把快门从 1/25 改成了 1/30\n\n**当前逻辑（每次都读Shutter）**：\n```python\ndelay1 = calc_stable_delay(client)  # 读1/25, 等1.5s\nsleep(delay1)\n_capture_and_crop(client, ...)  # 自动读快速门1/30, 再等1.55s\n```\n- 第1步：读1/25, 等1.5s\n- ...\n- 第5步：读1/25/1/30... 实际读到的是当前快门\n\n**优化后（缓存Shutter）**：\n```python\n_client_shutter_cached = calc_stable_delay(client)  # 第一次读1/25, 缓存\nsleep(_client_shutter_cached)  # 如果搜索到第5步（快门已变1/30）, 等的还是1.5s\n_capture_and_crop(client, skip_delay=True, ...)  # 不再读快门, 不再等\n```\n- 第1步：读1/25, 等1.5s（缓存）\n- ...\n- 第10步：快门已是1/30, 但等的还是1.5s（没读）\n- 搜索结束后：设备快门1/30, 但白平衡的收敛判断用的是1.5s的假设\n\n**问题**：\n- `calc_stable_delay` 被1次调用，缓存后，之后的延迟就固定了\n- 如果搜索中途快门变了，延迟就不匹配，可能导致：\n  - 截图时机不准确\n  - 白平衡收敛判断不准确（因为假设的delay不对）\n  - 切换回自动白平衡时，锁定状态可能有问题\n\n---\n\n## 评估影响\n\n**快门通常在什么情况下会变？**\n- 用户手动调整（极少在搜索期间）\n- 自动曝光模式（通常会动态调整）\n- 定时白平衡搜索之间（如果定时器没停，可能变成搜索）\n\n如果不是搜索期间，定时器已停或手动暂停了，那快门变动的概率很低。\n\n**延迟差异影响多大？**\n- 快门变化幅度：1/25 (0.04s) → 1/30 (0.033s) → 相差0.007s\n- calc_stable_delay = 1.5s + 快门 = 1.5s~1.507s (差异0.7%)\n- 对最终白平衡结果影响极小\n\n**但问题2：搜索结束后锁定，新一轮搜索以当前值为起点**\n- 第10步结束时：设备快门1/30, 白平衡收敛判断用了1.5s（假设快门1/25）\n- 但之后切换到自动/手动模式，快门仍是1/30\n- 新一轮搜索：快门1/30, 但延迟仍用1.5s... 等等！calc_stable_delay 又在读快门了！\n\n哦！我理解错了。缓存的 Shutter 是在 `WhiteBalanceSearcher` 实例级别，搜索结束后实例销毁。即使设备快门变了，下次启动新的 `WhiteBalanceSearcher` 时，还是会重新读快门。\n\n所以老板担心的\"搜索 中途快门变化后又回来\"这个场景很少发生。\n\n---\n\n## 重新评估优化方案的合理性\n\n**关键理解**：\n1. 缓存的 Shutter 只在**单次搜索会话**内有效\n2. 一旦搜索结束，`WhiteBalanceSearcher` 实例销毁，缓存失效\n3. 下次新搜索时，重新读 Shutter\n\n**场景验证**：\n- 第1次搜索：快门1/25，用1.5s延迟，搜索需要10步，结束后锁定\n- 用户手动改快门 → 1/30\n- 第2次搜索：新的 `WhiteBalanceSearcher` 实例，重新读快门1/30，用1.507s延迟\n\n所以缓存没有问题，因为它是**会话级**的，不是全局缓存的。\n\n那优化方案2（skip_delay=True）是合理的：\n```python\n# run() 中：读1次Shutter，等1次delay，截图\ndelay = calc_stable_delay(client)\nsleep(delay)\nbgr, _ = await asyncio.to_thread(self._capture, skip_delay=True)\n```\n\n这里的问题是：截图时可能快门已经变了，但没重新读。\n\n但这个影响很小，因为：\n1. 快门极少在搜索期间变化\n2. 即使变了，延迟差异0.7%，影响极小\n3. 截图本身就有IO延迟，不在毫秒级\n\n**结论**：优化方案2是合理的，不影响业务逻辑。\n\n但如果老板不放心，可以改回：不让缓存的 delay 影响截图时机（比如在 crop 前再读一次快门调整 delay）。\n\n---\n\n## 最优方案（保守）\n\n**方案A（激进）**：\n1. 搜索期间暂停轮询\n2. skip_delay=True\n3. 缓存 Shutter\n\n**方案B（保守）**：\n1. 搜索期间暂停轮询\n2. 不skip_delay，但把 calc_stable_delay 从 region_base.py 移到 whitebalance.py，run() 中复用\n3. 不缓存 Shutter，每次都读\n\n**方案B的效果**：每步4次交互 → 3次（节省1次GET），不影响快门动态适应\n\n需要实施哪个方案？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":94444,"output":1710,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96154,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783436552667,"responseId":"cht000d91ec@dx19f3d1a41cb29bb503"}}
