{"type":"message","id":"59d59e17","parentId":"a787db62","timestamp":"2026-07-07T16:56:08.319Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了！慢快门倍率通过 `/Image/channels/1/DSS` 端点读取：\n```xml\n<DSS>\n  <enabled>true</enabled>\n  <DSSLevel>1</DSSLevel>\n</DSS>\n```\n\n其中 `DSSLevel` 就是慢快门倍率。基础快门是 1/25，所以：\n- DSSLevel = 1 → 快门 = 1/25 * 1 = 0.04s\n- DSSLevel = 2 → 快门 = 1/25 * 2 = 0.08s\n- DSSLevel = 4 → 快门 = 1/25 * 4 = 0.16s\n\n所以正确的逻辑是：\n1. 测试 `/Image/channels/1/DSS`，看看慢快门是否支持\n2. 如果支持，读取 `DSSLevel` 值（如 \"1\", \"2\", \"4\"）\n3. 快门时间 = 1/25 * DSSLevel秒数\n4. 如果不支持，快门时间 = 1/25\n\n但现在 `get_exposure_time` 读的是 `/Image/channels/1/Shutter` 的 min/max limit，这是不对的。\n\n老板要求的完整逻辑应该是：\n1. 读取慢快门（DSS）\n2. 如果 DSS 支持，快门时间 = 1/25 * DSSLevel\n3. 否则，快门时间 = 1/25\n\n让我修改 `get_exposure_time` 为 `get_exposure_time_and_stable_delay`，或者把慢快门倍率计算和延迟计算分离。\n\n\n我将设计一个新的函数 `get_slow_shutter_factor`，专门处理慢快门倍率计算。这个函数将检查 DSS 端点，返回具体的快门系数值。主要目标是简化计算逻辑，提高代码的可读性和可维护性。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"找到了！慢快门倍率通过 **DSS** 读取：\n- 端点：`/Image/channels/1/DSS`\n- 字段：`DSSLevel`（如 \"1\", \"2\", \"4\"）\n- 基础快门：1/25 = 0.04s\n\n**正确的计算逻辑应该是**：\n1. 读 `/Image/channels/1/DSS`\n2. 如果 DSS 支持（enabled=true），慢快门倍率 = DSSLevel\n3. 快门时间 = 1/25 × 倍率\n4. 等待时间 = 1.5s + 快门时间\n\n现在开始全面修改。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_38abc15ec3c64243a0ba93e2","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"def get_exposure_time(client) -> float:\n    \"\"\"获取慢快门倍率系数 - v8.64:\n    基础快门1/25=0.04s。检查慢快门DSS。\n    返回慢快门倍率（无慢快门返回1）。\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/DSS\")\n        if resp.status_code == 200:\n            import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n            root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\n            for elem in root.iter():\n                tag = elem.tag.split('}')[-1] if '}' in elem.tag else elem.tag\n                if tag in (\"DSSLevel\", \"dssLevel\"):\n                    dss_level = (elem.text or \"0\").strip()\n                    try:\n                        level = int(dss_level)\n                        if level > 1:\n                            return float(level)  # v8.64: 返回倍率\n                    except ValueError:\n                        pass\n                    break  # 找到 DSSLevel 就退出了 (enabled 会包含在遍历中)\n    except:\n        pass\n    return 1.0  # 无慢快门，返回1倍","oldText":"def get_exposure_time(client) -> float:\n    \"\"\"获取慢快门额外曝光时间（秒）。\n\n    基础快门 1/25=0.04s。检查慢快门是否开启。\n    返回慢快门额外时间（无慢快门返回0）。\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/Shutter\")\n        if resp.status_code != 200:\n            return 0.0\n\n        import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n        root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\n\n        min_limit = None\n        max_limit = None\n\n        for elem in root.iter():\n            tag = elem.tag.split('}')[-1] if '}' in elem.tag else elem.tag\n            if tag in (\"minShutterLevelLimit\", \"MinShutterLevelLimit\"):\n                min_limit = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\n            elif tag in (\"maxShutterLevelLimit\", \"MaxShutterLevelLimit\"):\n                max_limit = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\n\n        if min_limit and max_limit and min_limit != max_limit:\n            min_time = _parse_shutter_level(min_limit)\n            max_time = _parse_shutter_level(max_limit)\n            if min_time > 0 and max_time > min_time:\n                return max_time - min_time\n\n        return 0.0\n    except Exception:\n        return 0.0"},{"newText":"def calc_stable_delay(client) -> float:\n    \"\"\"计算操作后的稳定延时 - v8.64:\n    等待时间 = 固定1.5s + 快门时间\n    快门时间 = 基础1/25 × 慢快门倍率。\n    \"\"\"\n    shutter_factor = get_exposure_time(client)  # v8.64: 获取倍率为1~N\n    base_shutter = 1/25  # 0.04s\n    shutter_time = base_shutter * shutter_factor  # 0.04 × 倍率\n    return 1.5 + shutter_time","oldText":"def calc_stable_delay(client) -> float:\n    \"\"\"计算操作后的稳定延时。\n\n    公式: 固定1.5s + 1/25 × 慢快门倍率（如果有）\n    \"\"\"\n    slow_extra = get_exposure_time(client)\n    return 1.5 + slow_extra"},{"newText":"\"\"\"AstroHub v8.64 - 画面分析基础工具\n\n提供：\n- _valid_pixels() - 排除死黑(0,0,0)和死白(255,255,255)的像素\n- _rgb_stats() - 计算RGB统计信息\n- calc_contrast() - 计算反差值（Laplacian方差的float）\n- get_exposure_time() - 获取慢快门倍率系数\n- calc_stable_delay() - 计算稳定延时 = 基础延迟1.5s + 快门时间\n\"\"\"","oldText":"\"\"\"AstroHub v8.60 - 画面分析基础工具\n\n提供：\n- _valid_pixels() - 排除死黑(0,0,0)和死白(255,255,255)的像素\n- _rgb_stats() - 计算RGB统计信息\n- calc_contrast() - 计算反差值（Laplacian方差的float）\n- get_exposure_time() - 获取曝光时间（固定1/25，检查慢快门）\n- calc_stable_delay() - 计算稳定延时 = 基础延迟1.5s + 慢快门额外时间\n\"\"\""}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\controlpanel\\region_base.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":122886,"output":1754,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":124640,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783443254181,"responseId":"cht000d4e1f@dx19f3d807b7829bb503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1244d071","parentId":"59d59e17","timestamp":"2026-07-07T16:56:08.345Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_38abc15ec3c64243a0ba93e2","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"edit\",\n  \"error\": \"Could not find edits[0] in C:\\\\Users\\\\admin\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\dev-factory\\\\astrohub\\\\src\\\\controlpanel\\\\region_base.py. The oldText must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"edit","error":"Could not find edits[0] in C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\controlpanel\\region_base.py. The oldText must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines."},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783443368345}}
{"type":"message","id":"a36bac0b","parentId":"1244d071","timestamp":"2026-07-07T16:57:06.773Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_af9c86e45ad0463f9314e176","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"offset":1,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\controlpanel\\region_base.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":124439,"output":48,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":124487,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783443368347,"responseId":"cht000decc5@dx19f3d83004029c2503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"fd1e2b7c","parentId":"a36bac0b","timestamp":"2026-07-07T16:57:06.779Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_af9c86e45ad0463f9314e176","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"AstroHub v8.60 - 画面分析基础工具\n\n提供：\n- _valid_pixels() - 排除死黑(0,0,0)和死白(255,255,255)的像素\n- _rgb_stats() - 计算RGB统计信息\n- calc_contrast() - 计算反差值（Laplacian方差的float）\n- get_exposure_time() - 获取曝光时间（固定1/25，检查慢快门）\n- calc_stable_delay() - 计算稳定延时 = 基础延迟1.5s + 慢快门额外时间\n\"\"\"\n\nimport cv2\nimport numpy as np\n\n\ndef _valid_pixels(bgr: np.ndarray):\n    \"\"\"排除死黑(0,0,0)和死白(255,255,255)，返回(B, G, R)三通道有效像素数组和计数。\"\"\"\n    dead_black = np.all(bgr == 0, axis=2)\n    dead_white = np.all(bgr == 255, axis=2)\n    valid = ~(dead_black | dead_white)\n    n = np.count_nonzero(valid)\n    if n < 10:\n        return None, None, None, None, 0\n    return bgr[:, :, 0][valid], bgr[:, :, 1][valid], bgr[:, :, 2][valid], valid, n\n\n\ndef _rgb_stats(bgr: np.ndarray) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"计算框选区域有效像素的RGB统计。\"\"\"\n    b_ch, g_ch, r_ch, _, n = _valid_pixels(bgr)\n    b_sum, g_sum, r_sum = float(b_ch.sum()), float(g_ch.sum()), float(r_ch.sum())\n    b_avg, g_avg, r_avg = float(b_ch.mean()), float(g_ch.mean()), float(r_ch.mean())\n    return {\n        \"n\": n,\n        \"b_sum\": b_sum,\n        \"g_sum\": g_sum,\n        \"r_sum\": r_sum,\n        \"b_avg\": b_avg,\n        \"g_avg\": g_avg,\n        \"r_avg\": r_avg\n    }\n\n\ndef calc_contrast(bgr: np.ndarray) -> float:\n    \"\"\"计算框选区域的反差值（Laplacian方差）。\"\"\"\n    gray = cv2.cvtColor(bgr, cv2.COLOR_BGR2GRAY)\n    return float(cv2.Laplacian(gray, cv2.CV_64F).var())\n\n\ndef _parse_shutter_level(level_str: str) -> float:\n    \"\"\"解析快门值字符串为秒数。\"\"\"\n    try:\n        level_str = level_str.strip()\n        if \"/\" in level_str:\n            num, den = level_str.split(\"/\")\n            return float(num) / float(den)\n        return float(level_str)\n    except (ValueError, ZeroDivisionError):\n        return 0.04\n\n\ndef get_exposure_time(client) -> float:\n    \"\"\"获取慢快门额外曝光时间（秒）。\n\n    基础快门 1/25=0.04s。检查慢快门是否开启。\n    返回慢快门额外时间（无慢快门返回0）。\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/Shutter\")\n        if resp.status_code != 200:\n            return 0.0\n\n        import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n        root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\n\n        min_limit = None\n        max_limit = None\n\n        for elem in root.iter():\n            tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\n            if tag in (\"minShutterLevelLimit\", \"MinShutterLevelLimit\"):\n                min_limit = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\n            elif tag in (\"maxShutterLevelLimit\", \"MaxShutterLevelLimit\"):\n                max_limit = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\n\n        if min_limit and max_limit and min_limit != max_limit:\n            min_time = _parse_shutter_level(min_limit)\n            max_time = _parse_shutter_level(max_limit)\n            if min_time > 0 and max_time > min_time:\n                return max_time - min_time\n\n        return 0.0\n    except Exception:\n        return 0.0\n\n\ndef calc_stable_delay(client) -> float:\n    \"\"\"计算操作后的稳定延时。\n\n    公式: 固定1.5s + 1/25 × 慢快门倍率（如果有）\n    \"\"\"\n    slow_extra = get_exposure_time(client)\n\n[2 more lines in file. Use offset=101 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783443426779}}
{"type":"message","id":"21b04b8e","parentId":"fd1e2b7c","timestamp":"2026-07-07T16:57:41.953Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_489defa83d0548eea2ba646b","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"\"\"\"AstroHub v8.64 - 画面分析基础工具\n\n提供：\n- _valid_pixels() - 排除死黑(0,0,0)和死白(255,255,255)的像素\n- _rgb_stats() - 计算RGB统计信息\n- calc_contrast() - 计算反差值（Laplacian方差的float）\n- get_exposure_time() - 获取慢快门倍率系数\n- calc_stable_delay() - 计算稳定延时 = 基础延迟1.5s + 快门时间\n\"\"\"","oldText":"\"\"\"AstroHub v8.60 - 画面分析基础工具\n\n提供：\n- _valid_pixels() - 排除死黑(0,0,0)和死白(255,255,255)的像素\n- _rgb_stats() - 计算RGB统计信息\n- calc_contrast() - 计算反差值（Laplacian方差的float）\n- get_exposure_time() - 获取曝光时间（固定1/25，检查慢快门）\n- calc_stable_delay() - 计算稳定延时 = 基础延迟1.5s + 慢快门额外时间\n\"\"\""},{"newText":"def get_exposure_time(client) -> float:\n    \"\"\"获取慢快门倍率系数 - v8.64:\n    基础快门1/25=0.04s。检查慢快门DSS。\n    返回慢快门倍率（无慢快门返回1）。\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/DSS\")\n        if resp.status_code == 200:\n            import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n            root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\n            for elem in root.iter():\n                tag = elem.tag.split('}')[-1] if '}' in elem.tag else elem.tag\n                if tag in (\"DSSLevel\", \"dssLevel\"):\n                    dss_level = (elem.text or \"0\").strip()\n                    try:\n                        level = int(dss_level)\n                        if level > 1:\n                            return float(level)  # v8.64: 返回倍率\n                    except ValueError:\n                        pass\n                    break\n    except:\n        pass\n    return 1.0  # 无慢快门，返回1倍","oldText":"def get_exposure_time(client) -> float:\n    \"\"\"获取慢快门额外曝光时间（秒）。\n\n    基础快门 1/25=0.04s。检查慢快门是否开启。\n    返回慢快门额外时间（无慢快门返回0）。\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/Shutter\")\n        if resp.status_code != 200:\n            return 0.0\n\n        import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n        root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\n\n        min_limit = None\n        max_limit = None\n\n        for elem in root.iter():\n            tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\n            if tag in (\"minShutterLevelLimit\", \"MinShutterLevelLimit\"):\n                min_limit = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\n            elif tag in (\"maxShutterLevelLimit\", \"MaxShutterLevelLimit\"):\n                max_limit = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\n\n        if min_limit and max_limit and min_limit != max_limit:\n            min_time = _parse_shutter_level(min_limit)\n            max_time = _parse_shutter_level(max_limit)\n            if min_time > 0 and max_time > min_time:\n                return max_time - min_time\n\n        return 0.0\n    except Exception:\n        return 0.0"},{"newText":"def calc_stable_delay(client) -> float:\n    \"\"\"计算操作后的稳定延时 - v8.64:\n    等待时间 = 固定1.5s + 快门时间\n    快门时间 = 基础1/25 × 慢快门倍率\n    \"\"\"\n    shutter_factor = get_exposure_time(client)  # v8.64: 倍率1~N\n    base_shutter = 1.0 / 25.0  # 0.04s\n    shutter_time = base_shutter * shutter_factor\n    return 1.5 + shutter_time","oldText":"def calc_stable_delay(client) -> float:\n    \"\"\"计算操作后的稳定延时。\n\n    公式: 固定1.5s + 1/25 × 慢快门倍率（如果有）\n    \"\"\"\n    slow_extra = get_exposure_time(client)\n    return 1.5 + slow_extra"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\controlpanel\\region_base.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":125733,"output":1176,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126909,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783443426782,"responseId":"cht000def6e@dx19f3d832dd329c2503"}}
