{"type":"message","id":"2521d677","parentId":"ddd82e79","timestamp":"2026-07-07T17:07:23.384Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我已经修改了定时搜索的逻辑，在开始时调用 `stopPtzImagePoll()`，在结束时（包括成功和失败）都调用 `startPtzImagePoll()`。\n\n老板问\"完成了？\"，我应该回答：完成了。然后总结一下所有的修改。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"完成！\n\n## 修改总结（v8.65）\n\n### 1. 快门速度只读一次\n**文件**: `whitebalance.py`, `autofocus.py`\n**修改**:\n- 搜索开始时：`self._stable_delay = calc_stable_delay(self.client)`\n- 后续调用：每步等 `self._stable_delay` 再截图，不再重复读快门\n\n### 2. 暂停主控台读取\n**文件**: `console.html` - `executeScheduledSearch()` 函数  \n**修改**:\n- 开始定时搜索：`stopPtzImagePoll()`\n- 搜索完成（无论成功/失败）：`startPtzImagePoll()`\n\n### 3. 正确的快门时间计算\n**文件**: `region_base.py`\n\n**修改前**:\n- 读 `/Image/channels/1/Shutter` 的 min/max limit\n- `calc_stable_delay = 1.5 + (max - min)`\n\n**修改后**:\n- 读 `/Image/channels/1/DSS` 的 `DSSLevel`（慢快门倍率）\n- `快门时间 = 1/25 × 倍率`\n- `calc_stable_delay = 1.5 + 快门时间`\n\n**示例**:\n- 无慢快门：倍率=1，快门=0.04s，延迟=1.54s\n- DSSLevel=2：倍率=2，快门=0.08s，延迟=1.58s\n- DSSLevel=4：倍率=4，快门=0.16s，延迟=1.66s\n\n**版本**: v8.64 → v8.65\n\n**备份**: `backup_20260708_0000/`"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":126455,"output":437,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126892,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783443982339,"responseId":"cht000d5670@dx19f3d8b9b4d2871503"}}
