{"type":"message","id":"677374e9","parentId":"22d190c2","timestamp":"2026-07-07T17:10:28.719Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板问：现在，开始局部自动对焦和局部白平衡，暂停主控台轮询，已经实现了吗\n\n我只修改了定时搜索（executeScheduledSearch），但没有修改手动搜索的逻辑。\n\n手动搜索的逻辑在哪里？让我回忆一下：\n- 白平衡开始搜索：应该在 `setWbMode('local')` 或开始框架选择时\n- 对焦开始搜索：应该在 `matchFocusContinuously` 或开始框架选择时\n\n我需要找到手动搜索的入口点。\n\n从之前看到的代码：\n- 对焦手动搜索：`matchFocusContinuously` 函数\n- 白平衡手动搜索：可能在框架选择后直接调用 search endpoint\n\n让我搜索一下手动搜索的入口点。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"老板，我**还没实现**。我只修改了定时搜索（`executeScheduledSearch`），但手动搜索没有添加暂停轮询逻辑。\n\n让我找到手动搜索的入口点："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_af40f58d8a9e4855874f2fd4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && Select-String -Path \"src/web/includes/console.html\" -Pattern \"whitebalance-search|matchFocusContinuously|startWBSearch|startFocusSearch\" -Context 2,2 | ForEach-Object { \"$($_.LineNumber): $($_.Line.TrimSpace())\" }"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":127065,"output":269,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127334,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783444136816,"responseId":"cht000d91c9@dx19f3d8e8bb829c2503"}}
