{"type":"message","id":"1f3b9076","parentId":"9db60336","timestamp":"2026-07-07T17:44:20.545Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"完成。总结修改：\n\n## v8.65 修改清单\n\n### 后端\n\n**`region_base.py`**：\n- `get_exposure_time()` → 读 `/Image/channels/1/DSS` 获取倍率，返回 1~N\n- `calc_stable_delay()` → `1.5 + (1/25 × 倍率)`\n\n**`whitebalance.py`**：\n- `WhiteBalanceSearcher.__init__` → 新增 `_stable_delay` 属性\n- `run()` → 开始时读一次快门缓存，后续用缓存值，不再重复读\n- `_capture()` → 传 `skip_delay=True`，跳过截图函数内部重复的延迟\n- 中断处理 → 从 `wb._best_red/_best_blue` 获取（修复原有 bug）\n\n**`autofocus.py`**：\n- 同白平衡，快门只读一次 + `_capture()` 传 `skip_delay=True`\n\n**`router.py`**：\n- `_capture_and_crop()` → 新增 `skip_delay` 参数\n\n### 前端\n\n**`index.html`（`_finishRegion`，手动框选入口）**：\n- 流程开始（fetch前）→ `stopPtzImagePoll()`\n- 流程结束（done/cleanup/error/interrupt/catch）→ `startPtzImagePoll()`\n\n**`console.html`（`executeScheduledSearch`，定时入口）**：\n- 流程开始 → `stopPtzImagePoll()`\n- 流程结束（then/catch）→ `startPtzImagePoll()`\n\n**`console.html`（`onWbModeChange` / `onFocusModeChange`）**：\n- 清理了我之前加的所有轮询代码，恢复干净\n\n### 版本号\nv8.63 → v8.65"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":143711,"output":391,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":144102,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783446193327,"responseId":"cht000dc1bb@dx19f3dae25902872503"}}
